WEBVTT

1
00:00:29.029 --> 00:00:43.660
♪♪♪♪

2
00:00:53.053 --> 00:00:58.058
[ Synchronized Yelling ]

3
00:00:58.058 --> 00:01:00.560
[ Continue Yelling ]

4
00:01:28.955 --> 00:01:31.458
[ Crowd Applauding ]

5
00:01:31.458 --> 00:01:35.345
WATCH WHERE YOU'RE GOING.
WE'RE ALMOST THERE.
SEE ?

6
00:01:45.855 --> 00:01:50.360
MOM. WHERE'S PAPA ?
I'M SURE HE'LL BE HERE SOON.
TAKE IT EASY.

7
00:01:50.860 --> 00:01:54.364
[ Announcer ]  WELCOME
TO THE 18th YOUTH MARTIAL ARTS
TOURNAMENT OF CHAMPIONS.

8
00:01:54.864 --> 00:01:56.366
COMPETING TODAY WILL BE--

9
00:01:56.366 --> 00:01:59.869
I'VE ONLY GOT
ONE MORE STOP.
ALL RIGHT.

10
00:02:00.370 --> 00:02:01.871
IT'S ALL YOURS.

11
00:02:01.871 --> 00:02:04.874
[ Bicycle Bell Ringing ]

12
00:02:10.380 --> 00:02:12.882
[ Line Ringing ]

13
00:02:12.882 --> 00:02:16.886
HEY. IT'S ME.  I'VE BEEN
WAITING HALF AN HOUR.
I'M OUT OF HERE. NOW.

14
00:02:16.886 --> 00:02:18.888
[ Man Over Phone ]
FORGET IT.  JUST KEEP WAITING.

15
00:02:18.888 --> 00:02:23.393
IT'S PART OF THE JOB.
OH. COME ON.  I'M SUPPOSED
TO BE WATCHING MY SON.

16
00:02:23.393 --> 00:02:25.395
[ Man Over Phone ]
WATCH HIM ANOTHER TIME.

17
00:02:25.395 --> 00:02:29.399
AH.  WELL. YOU KNOW WHAT ?
THESE GUYS GET
FIVE MORE MINUTES.

18
00:02:29.399 --> 00:02:34.404
NOW JUST A DAMN MINUTE. KUNG.
YOU WAIT UNTIL THEY SHOW UP
OR YOU'LL BE BACK IN UNIFORM...

19
00:02:34.904 --> 00:02:37.407
ON THE STREET.
GIVE IT A REST.
THEY'RE HERE.

20
00:02:37.407 --> 00:02:42.412
OKAY. I WANT THE GOODS.
BUT I WANT XIANG TOO.

21
00:02:42.412 --> 00:02:44.414
TRY NOT TO SCREW IT UP.

22
00:02:45.915 --> 00:02:47.917
NICE OF YOU TO SHOW UP.

23
00:02:47.917 --> 00:02:50.920
DON'T ANY OF YOU BIG-TIME
CRIMINALS OWN A WATCH ?

24
00:02:50.920 --> 00:02:54.924
WATCH YOUR MOUTH.
IT TAKES TIME
TO PRODUCE WORK THIS GOOD.

25
00:02:54.924 --> 00:02:57.427
FIFTEEN PASSPORTS.

26
00:02:57.794 --> 00:03:00.296
TAKE A LOOK.
ALL WESTERN.

27
00:03:00.296 --> 00:03:02.799
LET'S SEE THE MONEY.
THEY'RE VERY WELL MADE.

28
00:03:02.799 --> 00:03:04.801
ALL RIGHT.

29
00:03:04.801 --> 00:03:07.303
SIX APIECE.
A LITTLE MORE.

30
00:03:07.303 --> 00:03:09.305
SEVEN.

31
00:03:19.315 --> 00:03:21.818
- [ Thugs Gasp ]
- YOU'LL NEVER GET
  TO SPEND THIS MONEY.

32
00:03:21.818 --> 00:03:23.820
NOW YOU'RE DEAD.

33
00:03:23.820 --> 00:03:25.822
[ Grunting ]

34
00:03:27.323 --> 00:03:32.829
[ Thugs Yelling. Grunting ]

35
00:03:34.330 --> 00:03:36.833
HERE. JOHNNY.
HAVE SOME WATER.
NO.

36
00:03:36.833 --> 00:03:39.836
MAMA. WHERE'S PAPA ?

37
00:03:42.338 --> 00:03:45.842
[ Yelling. Groans ]

38
00:03:45.842 --> 00:03:47.844
[ Announcer ]
EIGHT. SIX. NINE--

39
00:03:47.844 --> 00:03:50.847
[ Yelling ]

40
00:03:51.347 --> 00:03:53.349
YOU'RE COMING WITH ME.
[ Groaning ]

41
00:03:53.349 --> 00:03:55.351
[ Continues Groaning ]

42
00:03:55.351 --> 00:03:58.354
[ Groaning ]
KEEP QUIET !

43
00:03:58.354 --> 00:04:02.358
[ Tournament Announcer ]
OUR FIRST SEMIFINALIST.
JOHN KUNG.

44
00:04:21.261 --> 00:04:22.762
[ Announcer ]
AND NOW OUR FINALISTS.

45
00:04:23.263 --> 00:04:27.767
TIMOTHY HO
WILL TAKE ON JOHNNY KUNG
FOR THE CHAMPIONSHIP.

46
00:04:39.779 --> 00:04:42.782
- [ Grunts ]
- [ Yells ]

47
00:04:42.782 --> 00:04:45.285
[ Both Yelling ]

48
00:04:45.285 --> 00:04:49.289
[ Weapons Clashing.
  Yelling Continues ]

49
00:04:49.789 --> 00:04:51.791
[ Continue Yelling ]

50
00:04:58.798 --> 00:05:02.302
[ Man In Bag Muttering ]
IF I EVER GET OUT--

51
00:05:02.302 --> 00:05:04.804
[ Groaning ]

52
00:05:04.804 --> 00:05:07.423
[ Yelling ]

53
00:05:12.562 --> 00:05:15.064
[ Footsteps Running ]

54
00:05:33.583 --> 00:05:36.586
[ Both Yelling ]

55
00:05:36.586 --> 00:05:40.089
[ Weapons Clashing.
  Yelling Continues ]

56
00:05:40.089 --> 00:05:42.091
[ Yells ]

57
00:06:11.988 --> 00:06:16.993
[ Announcer ]
EIGHT. NINE. EIGHT. NINE.

58
00:06:17.994 --> 00:06:20.997
[ Applauding Continues ]

59
00:06:20.997 --> 00:06:23.383
[ Screaming ]

60
00:06:24.884 --> 00:06:26.886
[ Woman Yelling ]
STAY WHERE YOU ARE !

61
00:06:26.886 --> 00:06:31.257
[ Crowd Clamoring ]

62
00:06:35.261 --> 00:06:38.264
MOM. WAIT HERE.
JOHNNY !

63
00:06:46.272 --> 00:06:47.774
- JOHNNY !
-[ Ax Man Grunting ]

64
00:06:50.777 --> 00:06:53.279
[ Yells ]

65
00:06:53.279 --> 00:06:56.282
LET ME GO !
[ Groaning ]

66
00:06:56.282 --> 00:06:58.284
HEY.

67
00:06:58.284 --> 00:07:00.286
COME ON !
TO THE RIGHT !

68
00:07:00.286 --> 00:07:02.288
GET OFF OF ME. DAMN IT !
[ Groans ]

69
00:07:02.288 --> 00:07:04.290
[ Officers Chattering ]

70
00:07:04.290 --> 00:07:06.793
YOU CAN GO NOW.
GET HIM.
 GET HIM !

71
00:07:06.793 --> 00:07:09.796
MOVE BACK.
COME ON.  HUH ?
WHO ?  COME ON.

72
00:07:09.796 --> 00:07:12.298
JOHNNY.
WHAT HAPPENED ?
WHERE'S PAPA ?

73
00:07:12.298 --> 00:07:14.801
[ Man ]
HEY. THIS KID'S A HERO.

74
00:07:14.801 --> 00:07:18.805
[ Crowd Cheering ]

75
00:07:19.305 --> 00:07:22.809
[ Laughing ]
[ Continues Cheering ]

76
00:07:28.314 --> 00:07:31.017
[ Both Gargling ]

77
00:07:38.524 --> 00:07:41.027
[ Gargling ]

78
00:07:49.035 --> 00:07:52.038
[ Women Chatting ]

79
00:07:52.038 --> 00:07:54.040
GOOD MORNING.
[ Bicyclist ]
GOOD MORNING.

80
00:07:54.540 --> 00:07:57.043
HEY. THERE.
HI. JOHNNY.

81
00:07:57.043 --> 00:08:01.547
[ Women Continue Chatting ]

82
00:08:04.050 --> 00:08:06.052
TRY TO BEAT
YOUR DAD. JOHNNY.

83
00:08:06.052 --> 00:08:09.422
SEE YOU AT SCHOOL.
BYE.

84
00:08:27.323 --> 00:08:32.578
COME ON. NOW.
THAT'S ENOUGH SEA DRAGON.

85
00:08:32.578 --> 00:08:34.580
[ Gasps ]

86
00:08:34.580 --> 00:08:38.084
BOY. I DID IT GOOD TODAY.

87
00:08:38.084 --> 00:08:41.587
I DON'T KNOW WHY
YOU HAVE TO PRACTICE
BREATHING EVERY MORNING.

88
00:08:41.587 --> 00:08:45.591
IT'S GOOD FOR JOHNNY
TO DO THIS.  YOU NEVER KNOW
WHEN HE MIGHT NEED IT.

89
00:08:45.591 --> 00:08:47.593
IT SEEMS SILLY.
IT'S NOT.

90
00:08:47.593 --> 00:08:50.596
IT'S A GOOD EXERCISE
JUST IN CASE YOUR BOAT
GETS SUNK.

91
00:08:50.596 --> 00:08:55.101
YOU CAN'T BREATHE UNDERWATER.
BUT IF YOU KNOW HOW TO HOLD
YOUR BREATH. YOU'LL BE READY.

92
00:08:55.101 --> 00:08:58.604
ARE YOU READY ?
THE SCHOOL BUS IS HERE.

93
00:08:58.604 --> 00:09:00.606
COME ON.
I'LL WALK YOU TO THE BUS.

94
00:09:00.606 --> 00:09:02.608
ALL RIGHT. LET'S GO.

95
00:09:02.608 --> 00:09:05.111
YOU KNOW WHAT ?
I FORGOT I HAVE A MEETING
THIS MORNING.

96
00:09:05.111 --> 00:09:08.614
BUT. POP.
I'M GONNA GET MY AWARD
TODAY FROM THE MAYOR.

97
00:09:09.115 --> 00:09:11.617
I'LL BE THERE.
OKAY ?
OKAY.

98
00:09:12.118 --> 00:09:14.620
6:00.

99
00:09:18.124 --> 00:09:23.129
[ Johnny's Voice ]
POP. SEE YOU AT CITY HALL.
HAVE FUN TODAY.

100
00:09:35.641 --> 00:09:37.143
HEY !

101
00:09:41.147 --> 00:09:44.150
SORRY I'M LATE. JOHNNY.

102
00:09:44.150 --> 00:09:46.152
LET'S SEE.

103
00:09:51.657 --> 00:09:55.161
[ Mother ]
JOHNNY REALLY WANTED YOU
TO BE IN THE PICTURE.

104
00:09:55.161 --> 00:10:00.166
HE KEPT ON ASKING.
HE SAID HE WANTED
ALL OF US TO BE THERE.

105
00:10:00.166 --> 00:10:03.669
YOU STILL ANGRY ?
[ Coughing ]

106
00:10:03.669 --> 00:10:06.172
IS THIS MAKING YOU COUGH ?
I'M GONNA QUIT.

107
00:10:06.172 --> 00:10:08.674
HEY. SHAKE.
LET'S SHAKE ON IT.

108
00:10:08.674 --> 00:10:10.676
HONEST TO GOD ?
HONEST.

109
00:10:10.676 --> 00:10:14.180
GOOD.  WANT SOME
CHOCOLATE ?  HERE.

110
00:10:14.180 --> 00:10:16.182
[ Chuckling ]
[ Kung ]  BETTER THAN
CIGARETTES ANY DAY.

111
00:10:16.682 --> 00:10:18.684
[ Bus Brakes Squeaking ]
JOHNNY. SHOW YOUR PASS.

112
00:10:20.186 --> 00:10:23.689
HEY. THAT LINE'S TOO SLOW.
LET'S GET IN THIS ONE.

113
00:10:30.196 --> 00:10:34.700
- [ Bus Accelerates ]
- HEY. I GOT SOMETHING FOR YOU.

114
00:10:34.700 --> 00:10:37.703
HERE.
SEE ?

115
00:10:37.703 --> 00:10:40.206
MOM. DAD GAVE ME A WATCH.

116
00:10:40.706 --> 00:10:42.708
LOOK AT IT.
ISN'T IT COOL. MOM ?
LET ME HAVE A LOOK AT IT.

117
00:10:42.708 --> 00:10:44.710
LOOK !  ISN'T IT GREAT !
IT'S SO NICE.

118
00:10:44.710 --> 00:10:47.213
WHAT DO YOU THINK ?

119
00:10:47.213 --> 00:10:50.216
IS IT REALLY MINE ?
[ Laughs.
  Coughing ]

120
00:10:50.216 --> 00:10:54.220
HEY. CAN YOU BREATHE
ALL RIGHT ?
I'M FINE.

121
00:10:54.220 --> 00:10:56.222
ARE YOU SURE ?
I SAID I'M FINE.

122
00:10:56.722 --> 00:11:01.727
YOU DON'T LOOK FINE.
 YOU NEED YOUR MEDICINE ?
NO. I'LL BE ALL RIGHT.

123
00:11:01.727 --> 00:11:04.230
[ Clears Throat ]
SEE ?  I'M FEELING
BETTER ALREADY.

124
00:11:04.230 --> 00:11:08.234
SURE.  I BET IF YOU
SAT DOWN FOR A WHILE.
YOU'D FEEL A LOT BETTER.

125
00:11:08.234 --> 00:11:10.736
ALL RIGHT.
I GET IT.
THANKS.

126
00:11:10.736 --> 00:11:15.241
HERE. MOM.
SIT DOWN.
THANK YOU.

127
00:11:15.241 --> 00:11:17.743
HEY. MOM. YOU WANT
TO SEE MY ANTS ?

128
00:11:17.743 --> 00:11:19.745
WOW. JOHNNY.
WHERE DID YOU GET THOSE ?

129
00:11:19.745 --> 00:11:22.248
I GOT THEM
ON THE PLAYGROUND.
RIGHT AFTER MATH.

130
00:11:22.748 --> 00:11:25.251
YOU KNOW. JOHNNY.
I READ THAT A SOUP
MADE FROM ANTS...

131
00:11:25.251 --> 00:11:27.253
CAN BE USED TO TREAT
SOME BREATHING PROBLEMS.

132
00:11:27.253 --> 00:11:29.255
DID YOU KNOW THAT ?
UH-HUH.

133
00:11:29.255 --> 00:11:32.758
I LEARNED IT AT SCHOOL.
HEY. CAN I SHOW FREDDY
MY AWARD ?

134
00:11:32.758 --> 00:11:35.261
JOHNNY. WATCH OUT !

135
00:11:35.261 --> 00:11:37.263
IT'S THOSE MEN
OVER THERE--
FREDDY. WILL YOU STOP IT ?

136
00:11:37.263 --> 00:11:39.765
MOM. LET ME GO !
GET BACK IN THE HOUSE.
HOW MANY TIMES--

137
00:11:39.765 --> 00:11:42.268
[ Mother ]
WHAT WAS THAT ALL ABOUT ?
[ Johnny ]  I DON'T KNOW.

138
00:11:42.268 --> 00:11:44.270
IT'S JUST FREDDY.

139
00:11:45.271 --> 00:11:47.273
[ Man ]
THERE HE IS.
GET HIM.

140
00:11:47.273 --> 00:11:50.776
- WHAT ARE YOU GUYS DOING ?
- UP AGAINST THE WALL !

141
00:11:50.776 --> 00:11:53.279
[ Mother ]  WEI !  WEI !
WHAT ARE YOU DOING ?
PAPA !

142
00:11:53.779 --> 00:11:55.781
LET HIM GO !
[ Mother ]
WEI !  WEI !

143
00:11:55.781 --> 00:11:58.284
[ Johnny ]
THEY'RE TAKING AWAY MY DAD !

144
00:11:58.784 --> 00:12:00.286
BACK AWAY. PEOPLE.
[ Johnny ]
WHAT'S HAPPENING ?

145
00:12:00.786 --> 00:12:03.289
[ Soldier ]
MOVE AWAY.
LET US MOVE HERE.

146
00:12:05.791 --> 00:12:08.794
[ Siren Blaring ]

147
00:12:11.414 --> 00:12:13.416
[ Neighbors Chattering ]

148
00:12:13.916 --> 00:12:16.919
LET'S GO INSIDE.
THAT'S ENOUGH NOW.
BE QUIET.

149
00:12:16.919 --> 00:12:20.423
COME WITH ME.
IT'S ALL RIGHT.
COME ON.

150
00:12:20.423 --> 00:12:22.425
WE'RE GOING INSIDE.

151
00:12:30.433 --> 00:12:33.936
[ Chatting ]

152
00:12:33.936 --> 00:12:37.440
WE GOT YOU THIS TIME.
YOU'RE GOING AWAY. GI DOG.
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT ?

153
00:12:37.440 --> 00:12:39.442
I WAS JUST
HANGING OUT WITH HER.
IT'S HER DOPE.

154
00:12:39.442 --> 00:12:41.444
CUT THE CRAP.
YOU WERE HOLDING IT.
SO IT'S YOURS.

155
00:12:41.444 --> 00:12:44.447
I WANT TO TALK
TO A LAWYER.
I BET YOU DO.

156
00:12:45.448 --> 00:12:46.949
[ Punching.
  Groaning ]

157
00:12:46.949 --> 00:12:48.951
WHAT DO YOU THINK
YOU'RE DOING ?

158
00:12:48.951 --> 00:12:52.955
HEY. WHERE'S MY PHONE ?
I WANT TO TALK TO MY LAWYER.

159
00:12:52.955 --> 00:12:55.958
GET IN THERE.
YOU DIRTBAG.
[ Groans ]

160
00:12:55.958 --> 00:12:58.461
[ Cries Out ]

161
00:12:58.461 --> 00:13:00.463
[ Softly ]
WHO'S THAT ?
HUH ?

162
00:13:00.463 --> 00:13:02.965
OVER THERE.
IN THAT CELL.
OH. THAT'S GI DOG.

163
00:13:03.466 --> 00:13:05.468
HE WORKS FOR BO XIANG.
THE MOB BOSS.

164
00:13:05.468 --> 00:13:08.971
HE'S PART OF YOUR NEXT
UNDERCOVER ASSIGNMENT.
THAT'S WHY WE BROUGHT YOU IN.

165
00:13:08.971 --> 00:13:12.975
YOU CAN'T.  WHAT ABOUT
MY WIFE'S HEALTH. HUH ?

166
00:13:13.476 --> 00:13:15.478
WHAT HAPPENS
IF I REFUSE ?

167
00:13:15.478 --> 00:13:19.982
PUT THOSE IDEAS
OUT OF YOUR HEAD.
IT'S JUST FOR A FEW WEEKS.

168
00:13:19.982 --> 00:13:24.487
THEY'RE SENDING YOU BECAUSE YOU
SEEM TO HAVE SUCH A GOOD RAPPORT
WITH THOSE CRIMINAL TYPES.

169
00:13:24.987 --> 00:13:29.492
GET CLOSE TO GI DOG.
WE'LL SET UP YOUR ESCAPE
FOR TONIGHT.

170
00:13:34.497 --> 00:13:36.499
[ Yelling ]

171
00:13:36.499 --> 00:13:38.501
[ Gasping ]
HELP ME !

172
00:13:38.501 --> 00:13:40.503
[ Guard ]
WHAT'S GOING ON ?

173
00:13:40.503 --> 00:13:42.505
I'M COMING IN !
[ Continues Gasping ]
HELP ME !

174
00:13:45.508 --> 00:13:48.511
HEY. YOU !

175
00:13:50.012 --> 00:13:55.017
[ Gasps ]
HEY. HEY. HEY !  W-WAIT !

176
00:13:55.518 --> 00:13:58.020
[ Alarm Ringing ]

177
00:13:58.020 --> 00:14:00.523
I GOT
A BAD LEG.
COME ON. MOVE IT !

178
00:14:00.523 --> 00:14:03.025
[ Dogs Barking ]
[ Gasping ]
GUARD DOGS !

179
00:14:03.526 --> 00:14:07.029
- [ Dogs Barking ]
- [ Wei ]  COME ON !  FASTER !

180
00:14:09.031 --> 00:14:12.535
- THEY'RE CATCHING UP !
- [ Guard ]  THERE HE IS !

181
00:14:12.535 --> 00:14:15.538
GET THEM !
GET THEM !  HALT !
SHOOT THEM !

182
00:14:17.039 --> 00:14:19.041
[ Gasps ]

183
00:14:19.542 --> 00:14:23.045
- GET THEM !  COME ON !
- [ Screaming ]

184
00:14:23.045 --> 00:14:27.049
[ Dogs Snarling.
  Gi Dog Screaming ]

185
00:14:28.551 --> 00:14:31.053
[ Dogs Whimpering ]

186
00:14:33.556 --> 00:14:35.558
RUN !

187
00:14:41.063 --> 00:14:45.067
- [ Screams. Gasping ]
- LET'S GET GOING.

188
00:14:45.067 --> 00:14:49.071
[ Guards Shouting.
  Dogs Barking ]

189
00:14:58.280 --> 00:15:03.285
I TELL YOU. WITH A WIFE
AND KID TO TAKE CARE OF.
I'D BE MORE CAREFUL.

190
00:15:03.285 --> 00:15:07.289
BUT THANKS
FOR GETTING ME OUT.
YOU'RE ALL RIGHT.

191
00:15:07.289 --> 00:15:10.793
[ Coughing ]

192
00:15:10.793 --> 00:15:15.297
[ Coughing Continues ]

193
00:15:17.299 --> 00:15:21.303
[ Labored Breathing ]

194
00:15:25.307 --> 00:15:27.810
- POP.
- SHH.

195
00:15:27.810 --> 00:15:30.312
[ Coughing Continues ]

196
00:15:35.818 --> 00:15:37.820
YOU'RE BACK.

197
00:15:39.321 --> 00:15:41.824
SON. LISTEN.

198
00:15:42.324 --> 00:15:45.327
PAPA HAS TO MAKE
A LITTLE TRIP.

199
00:15:45.327 --> 00:15:49.832
MAKE SURE MOM
HAS EVERYTHING
SHE NEEDS.

200
00:15:49.832 --> 00:15:55.337
WILL YOU... TRY
TO TAKE CARE OF HER
WHILE I'M GONE ?

201
00:15:55.337 --> 00:15:58.340
HOW LONG
WILL YOU BE ?

202
00:16:04.346 --> 00:16:07.850
WE'RE GONNA BE BACK
BEFORE YOU KNOW IT.

203
00:16:07.850 --> 00:16:10.352
YOU WANT TO BE CAREFUL
NOT TO UPSET THE BOY;

204
00:16:10.352 --> 00:16:12.354
OTHERWISE.
HE'LL START CRYING
AND WAKE UP YOUR WIFE.

205
00:16:12.855 --> 00:16:14.857
I'M NOT GONNA CRY.

206
00:16:17.860 --> 00:16:20.863
MONEY. JOHNNY.

207
00:16:22.364 --> 00:16:24.366
GIVE IT TO YOUR MOM.

208
00:16:24.366 --> 00:16:28.370
DAD.
WHERE ARE YOU GOING ?
[ Sighs ]

209
00:16:31.874 --> 00:16:35.377
YOU GOTTA TELL THE KID
SOMETHING. RIGHT ?

210
00:16:39.882 --> 00:16:43.886
BUDDY.
JUST MAKE SOMETHING UP.
HE'S ONLY A KID.

211
00:16:45.888 --> 00:16:49.391
[ Wei ]
NO. I TELL ENOUGH LIES.

212
00:17:00.903 --> 00:17:04.907
EVERYTHING'S GONNA BE OKAY NOW.
POP WILL BE BACK SOON.

213
00:17:04.907 --> 00:17:06.909
[ Chuckles ]

214
00:17:06.909 --> 00:17:10.913
BUT WHILE HE'S GONE.
WHY DON'T YOU...
TAKE MY LUCKY RING ?

215
00:17:12.414 --> 00:17:16.418
- HE DOESN'T NEED IT.
- BUT IT'S GOOD LUCK.
  AT LEAST HE'LL HAVE SOMETHING.

216
00:17:16.418 --> 00:17:18.921
SAY THANK YOU.

217
00:17:18.921 --> 00:17:20.923
THANK YOU.

218
00:17:20.923 --> 00:17:23.425
ALL RIGHT.
 ALL RIGHT.
[ Dogs Barking ]

219
00:17:23.425 --> 00:17:28.430
OOH. WE'VE GOT
TO GET MOVING.
[ Barking Continues ]

220
00:17:28.430 --> 00:17:32.434
- PAPA !
-[ Barking Continues ]

221
00:17:41.944 --> 00:17:45.948
SEE YOU. KID.
HEY. HEY. YOU'RE NOT GONNA START
RUNNING AGAIN. ARE YOU ?

222
00:17:48.450 --> 00:17:50.953
I TOLD YOU BEFORE
I-I GOT A BAD LEG.

223
00:18:02.114 --> 00:18:05.617
[ Gi Dog ]
WE'RE IN HONG KONG NOW.
LIVE A LITTLE.

224
00:18:08.120 --> 00:18:10.622
HERE.
[ Gasps. Laughs ]

225
00:18:10.622 --> 00:18:14.126
HOW MUCH IS IT ?
[ Merchant ]
THREE HUNDRED. SIR.

226
00:18:14.126 --> 00:18:16.628
OH.
OH. HEY. HEY.
I'LL GET THAT.
HOW MUCH ?

227
00:18:16.628 --> 00:18:18.881
WAIT.
I GOT IT.

228
00:18:18.881 --> 00:18:21.383
SO WHEN DO WE MEET
YOUR BOSS ?

229
00:18:21.383 --> 00:18:23.385
DON'T WORRY.
IT'S ALL SET UP.

230
00:18:24.386 --> 00:18:27.389
HEY. YOU LIKE THAT ?

231
00:18:27.389 --> 00:18:31.393
I'LL STEAL IT
FOR YOU TOMORROW.
YEAH ?

232
00:18:31.393 --> 00:18:34.396
[ Honks Horn ]
HEY. GIRLS.
WHAT'S SHAKING. HUH ?

233
00:18:34.396 --> 00:18:36.398
GO HOME !
WHAT A LOSER.

234
00:18:36.398 --> 00:18:38.400
WE'LL STEAL THEM
TOMORROW TOO.

235
00:18:42.404 --> 00:18:48.410
I'M SET UP GOOD...
TO BUY SOME BOMBS.
PLASTIC EXPLOSIVES.

236
00:18:48.410 --> 00:18:51.413
THE ONLY THING IS.
I DON'T WANT TO PART WITH
THE $2-MILLION ASKING PRICE.

237
00:18:51.914 --> 00:18:55.918
NOW. THE WAY
I FIGURE IT.

238
00:18:56.418 --> 00:18:58.921
ONE OF YOU SMART GUYS...

239
00:18:59.421 --> 00:19:01.423
OUGHT TO BE ABLE
TO FIGURE OUT...

240
00:19:01.423 --> 00:19:03.425
THE WAY...

241
00:19:03.926 --> 00:19:05.427
TO DO IT.

242
00:19:05.928 --> 00:19:07.930
NOT ME.

243
00:19:07.930 --> 00:19:12.935
[ Groans ]
KEEP IT UP. AND I'LL
TAKE A BRICK TO YOUR FACE.

244
00:19:12.935 --> 00:19:14.937
SCUM.

245
00:19:14.937 --> 00:19:19.942
AND WE CATCH 'EM...
ALL AT ONCE.

246
00:19:19.942 --> 00:19:22.945
[ Chuckling ]
[ Bo ]
HEY.

247
00:19:22.945 --> 00:19:25.447
YOU GONNA EXPLAIN
YOUR BIG IDEA ?

248
00:19:25.948 --> 00:19:28.951
SURE.  STEP ONE:
WE GIVE THEM ALL
THE MONEY.

249
00:19:29.451 --> 00:19:31.453
THEN ONCE THEY HAND OVER
ALL THE EXPLOSIVES.

250
00:19:31.453 --> 00:19:33.455
WE SIMPLY GO BACK
FOR THE MONEY AND TAKE IT.

251
00:19:33.956 --> 00:19:36.959
SIMPLE.
ALMOST AS SIMPLE
AS YOU ARE.

252
00:19:39.461 --> 00:19:41.463
[ Gasping ]

253
00:19:45.968 --> 00:19:48.971
NO. NO.
DON'T LET ME FALL !
DON'T LET ME FALL !

254
00:19:48.971 --> 00:19:52.474
[ Whimpering ]
DON'T LET GO.
DON'T LET GO.

255
00:19:52.975 --> 00:19:57.479
YOU BETTER KEEP YOUR STUPID
IDEAS TO YOURSELF. MORON.

256
00:19:57.479 --> 00:19:59.481
HEY. LISTEN.

257
00:19:59.481 --> 00:20:03.485
WE CAN KEEP THE EXPLOSIVES
WITHOUT LOSING YOUR DOUGH.

258
00:20:03.485 --> 00:20:06.488
YEAH. YEAH.
THAT'S WHAT I'VE BEEN
TRYING TO TELL YOU !

259
00:20:06.488 --> 00:20:09.992
YEAH. YEAH.
[ Continues Whimpering ]

260
00:20:09.992 --> 00:20:15.497
OKAY.
LET'S HEAR IT. HUH ?

261
00:20:15.497 --> 00:20:18.000
YOU GO ALONE.

262
00:20:18.000 --> 00:20:20.002
THAT'S NOT MUCH
OF A PLAN.

263
00:20:20.002 --> 00:20:23.005
AT THE MEETING.
YOU GIVE THEM THE MONEY.
PICK UP THE EXPLOSIVES.

264
00:20:23.505 --> 00:20:27.009
ON YOUR SIGNAL.
THE REST OF US RUSH IN
AND TAKE THEM DOWN.

265
00:20:36.518 --> 00:20:40.022
[ Bo ]
WHAT'S GONNA STOP THEM
FROM BLOWING US AWAY ?

266
00:20:40.022 --> 00:20:43.525
THE SUIT MADE FROM EXPLOSIVES
THAT ONE OF US HAS ON.

267
00:20:47.029 --> 00:20:50.032
I'LL LET YOU WEAR IT.

268
00:20:50.032 --> 00:20:56.038
OKAY. TOMORROW.
BY THAT WATERFALL.
WAIT FOR MY SIGNAL.

269
00:20:59.942 --> 00:21:04.446
FIVE YEARS.  THAT'S HOW LONG
I'VE BEEN WAITING FOR YOU
TO LEAVE YOUR WIFE.

270
00:21:04.947 --> 00:21:08.951
IT'S NOT THAT EASY.
THESE THINGS TAKE TIME.

271
00:21:08.951 --> 00:21:11.453
OH. REALLY ?

272
00:21:11.453 --> 00:21:14.456
YOU KNOW
IT'S WHAT I WANT.

273
00:21:14.456 --> 00:21:18.961
YES.
SO YOU'VE TOLD ME.

274
00:21:30.472 --> 00:21:33.475
OH. MR. BO. YOUR FRIENDS
ARE ALREADY UPSTAIRS
WAITING FOR YOU.

275
00:21:33.475 --> 00:21:35.477
THANK YOU. DARLING.
THANK YOU.

276
00:21:36.979 --> 00:21:40.482
IF IT ISN'T THE FAMOUS
MR. BO XIANG HIMSELF.
STANLEY !

277
00:21:40.482 --> 00:21:43.485
MR. BO. JUST A FRIENDLY LITTLE
FRISK. IF YOU DON'T MIND.
HOW ARE YOU ?

278
00:21:43.485 --> 00:21:46.989
AS LONG AS YOU DON'T GET
TOO FRIENDLY OR TOO FRISKY.

279
00:21:46.989 --> 00:21:49.992
DON'T TOUCH.
YOU GOT IT.
[ Laughs ]

280
00:21:49.992 --> 00:21:51.493
HEY. THERE.

281
00:21:52.995 --> 00:21:54.997
PLEASE. SIT DOWN.

282
00:21:55.998 --> 00:21:59.001
HOW ARE YOU ?
I'M FINE.

283
00:22:00.002 --> 00:22:02.004
[ Bo ]
DON'T WORRY.

284
00:22:04.506 --> 00:22:06.508
I CAME BY MYSELF.

285
00:22:07.009 --> 00:22:09.511
SHALL WE GET THIS
OVER WITH ?

286
00:22:11.013 --> 00:22:14.516
THEY TOLD ME
YOU WERE DANGEROUS.

287
00:22:14.516 --> 00:22:18.020
YOU ARE NOTORIOUS
FOR DOUBLE-CROSSING.

288
00:22:26.778 --> 00:22:30.782
JUST LIKE A WOMAN:
SULKY. ANGRY.

289
00:22:31.283 --> 00:22:33.285
THEY'RE NEVER HAPPY.

290
00:22:33.785 --> 00:22:36.288
[ Gi ]
SO THAT'S YOUR BOMB. HUH ?

291
00:22:36.788 --> 00:22:39.291
[ Spits ]
SO IS THIS THING
GONNA BLOW UP OR WHAT ?

292
00:22:39.291 --> 00:22:41.793
SURE. IT WILL.
YEAH ?
OKAY.

293
00:22:44.296 --> 00:22:46.298
HEY. BUDDY...

294
00:22:46.298 --> 00:22:48.300
I JUST WANT TO SAY...

295
00:22:48.300 --> 00:22:51.803
WHEN A WOMAN'S IN CHARGE.
WATCH YOUR BACK.

296
00:22:52.304 --> 00:22:54.806
I'M SURE
HE'S FIGURED THAT OUT.

297
00:22:54.806 --> 00:22:57.809
NEXT TIME
YOU'RE IN LATVIA.
WE'LL BUY YOU A DRINK.

298
00:22:57.809 --> 00:23:00.812
OKAY. OKAY.
BE THERE OR BE SQUARE.

299
00:23:00.812 --> 00:23:03.815
LATER.
[ Laughing ]

300
00:23:04.316 --> 00:23:06.818
[ Engine Starts ]
YEAH.

301
00:23:11.323 --> 00:23:13.825
[ Bo ]
LET'S DO IT.

302
00:23:13.825 --> 00:23:16.328
READY.

303
00:23:16.328 --> 00:23:20.332
- [ Shutter Clicking ]
-[ Car Engine Starts ]

304
00:23:24.086 --> 00:23:25.587
NO PROBLEM.
AN EASY $2 MILLION .

305
00:23:27.089 --> 00:23:28.590
[ Laughing ]

306
00:23:32.094 --> 00:23:35.597
- WATCH THE KID !
- [ Woman Screaming ]

307
00:23:43.355 --> 00:23:47.359
[ Crowd Clamoring ]

308
00:23:52.481 --> 00:23:55.117
LET'S GO !

309
00:23:55.117 --> 00:23:57.235
GET TO THE CAR !
COME ON !  MOVE !

310
00:23:57.235 --> 00:24:00.739
- [ Gasps ]
-[ Crowd Continues Shouting ]

311
00:24:00.739 --> 00:24:03.241
[ Woman ]
WATCH OUT !
WATCH OUT !

312
00:24:03.742 --> 00:24:06.244
- COVER ME !  I'LL GET IT !
- THERE !  THERE !

313
00:24:06.244 --> 00:24:09.631
[ Exchanging Gunfire ]

314
00:24:09.631 --> 00:24:13.135
GET OUT OF THE WAY !
MOVE !  GET OUT OF HERE !

315
00:24:13.135 --> 00:24:15.637
- [ Glass Shatters ]
- [ Grunting ]

316
00:24:28.150 --> 00:24:32.654
GO. GO !  COME ON !
YOU CAN GO.  COME ON !

317
00:24:42.914 --> 00:24:45.167
DON'T MOVE !

318
00:24:47.169 --> 00:24:49.671
[ Sighs ]

319
00:24:49.671 --> 00:24:52.174
[ Chuckling ]

320
00:24:53.175 --> 00:24:55.677
DROP THE GUN
AND PUT DOWN THE SUITCASE.

321
00:24:59.681 --> 00:25:03.185
DROP THE FREAKIN' GUNS !

322
00:25:10.442 --> 00:25:12.561
GO AHEAD AND SHOOT !

323
00:25:12.561 --> 00:25:14.696
GO !  COME ON !

324
00:25:14.696 --> 00:25:17.699
LET'S SEE WHAT HAPPENS.
YOU KNOW THIS IS THE REAL THING.

325
00:25:20.202 --> 00:25:23.822
- THROW THE GUNS IN THE WATER.
- DON'T SHOOT !  DON'T SHOOT !

326
00:25:32.330 --> 00:25:34.332
HEY. WHAT'S UP ?
THEY'RE SHOOTING
INSIDE THERE.

327
00:25:34.332 --> 00:25:36.334
SHOOTING ?
STAY DOWN.

328
00:25:36.334 --> 00:25:39.337
[ Man ]  LET'S GO.
COME ON NOW.  CAREFUL.
GO.  QUICKLY.

329
00:25:41.840 --> 00:25:43.341
DON'T MOVE.

330
00:25:43.341 --> 00:25:45.844
CODE NINE.  SHOOTOUT
ON JUNCTION STREET.

331
00:25:45.844 --> 00:25:50.348
- QUICK.  LET'S GO.
-[ Men ]  COME ON. LET'S GO.
  LET'S GO. LET'S GO.

332
00:25:52.851 --> 00:25:54.853
GET OUT OF HERE !

333
00:26:01.860 --> 00:26:03.495
I GOT HIM !

334
00:26:04.996 --> 00:26:06.498
GET YOUR GUNS !

335
00:26:07.999 --> 00:26:10.001
NOW. NOW !

336
00:26:10.001 --> 00:26:13.004
[ Firing ]

337
00:26:13.004 --> 00:26:15.006
GET HIM !
[ Firing ]

338
00:26:15.507 --> 00:26:18.376
[ Screaming ]

339
00:26:18.376 --> 00:26:20.762
- [ Groans ]
- [ Gun Misfires ]

340
00:26:27.018 --> 00:26:31.139
[ Screaming ]

341
00:26:34.643 --> 00:26:36.144
[ Scream ]

342
00:26:48.406 --> 00:26:53.411
- [ Bullets Ricochetting ]
- [ Weapon Jams. Wei Gasps ]

343
00:26:55.413 --> 00:26:57.916
QUICK. LET'S GO !
GET OUT !
THIS WAY !

344
00:26:57.916 --> 00:27:02.304
[ Gunfire ]

345
00:27:02.304 --> 00:27:04.806
[ Gunfire Continues ]
[ Screaming ]

346
00:27:05.307 --> 00:27:08.310
[ Gunfire Continues ]

347
00:27:15.317 --> 00:27:20.322
[ Gunfire Continues ]

348
00:27:24.326 --> 00:27:26.828
-[ Gunfire Continues ]
- [ Bullets Ricochetting ]

349
00:27:29.331 --> 00:27:31.833
[ Siren Blaring ]

350
00:27:36.338 --> 00:27:38.340
STAY LOW.

351
00:27:38.340 --> 00:27:40.342
[ Siren Blaring.
  Crowd Clamoring ]

352
00:27:41.843 --> 00:27:46.097
HEY !  I'M A DETECTIVE !

353
00:27:47.098 --> 00:27:49.718
[ Gasps. Bullet Ricochets ]

354
00:27:51.720 --> 00:27:53.722
[ Drops Gun ]

355
00:27:57.225 --> 00:28:00.729
DROP THE GUN
OR I'LL KILL HIM.

356
00:28:00.729 --> 00:28:03.231
NOW.

357
00:28:09.120 --> 00:28:11.122
[ Sizzling ]

358
00:28:11.122 --> 00:28:15.126
- GET EVERYONE OUT !
- [ Crowd Shouting ]

359
00:28:22.133 --> 00:28:24.135
THAT MEANS YOU TOO.

360
00:28:25.637 --> 00:28:28.139
GO !

361
00:28:37.148 --> 00:28:40.652
WHAT NOW.
INSPECTOR FONG ?

362
00:28:40.652 --> 00:28:45.407
YOU BOYS BEHAVE NOW...
AND NOBODY GETS HURT.

363
00:28:45.407 --> 00:28:47.909
TAKE IT EASY NOW.

364
00:28:47.909 --> 00:28:50.412
[ Continues Sizzling ]
[ Tires Screeching ]

365
00:29:03.541 --> 00:29:06.544
STOP.  JUST LISTEN.

366
00:29:07.045 --> 00:29:09.047
DON'T YOU THINK AN INSPECTOR
WOULD MAKE A BETTER HOSTAGE ?

367
00:29:09.047 --> 00:29:11.049
TAKE ME INSTEAD.

368
00:29:13.551 --> 00:29:16.554
START DRIVING.

369
00:29:20.558 --> 00:29:24.562
[ Revving Engine ]

370
00:29:31.069 --> 00:29:33.204
THE BOMB !

371
00:29:49.220 --> 00:29:52.724
[ Wei ]
SO WHY DID YOU VOLUNTEER ?
YOU AN ACTION FREAK ?

372
00:29:52.724 --> 00:29:55.226
[ Fong ]
JAMES--
DETECTIVE SHU--

373
00:29:55.727 --> 00:29:59.230
WOULD HAVE DONE
SOMETHING... STUPID.

374
00:29:59.230 --> 00:30:01.232
AND YOU'D MAKE HIM PAY.

375
00:30:01.232 --> 00:30:04.235
BUT YOU WON'T TRY
ANYTHING STUPID. RIGHT ?
[ Siren Approaching ]

376
00:30:04.235 --> 00:30:07.739
NOT ME.

377
00:30:07.739 --> 00:30:11.743
[ Siren. Louder ]
DO YOU KNOW
WHERE YOU'RE GOING ?

378
00:30:11.743 --> 00:30:13.745
[ Fong ]
OH. YEAH.

379
00:30:26.624 --> 00:30:29.627
GET OUT !

380
00:30:30.128 --> 00:30:32.130
- [ Sirens Blaring ]
- [ Fires ]

381
00:30:34.015 --> 00:30:36.017
[ Gasps ]

382
00:30:45.643 --> 00:30:50.899
HOLD ON !
[ Groaning ]

383
00:30:51.399 --> 00:30:54.402
I'VE GOT YOU.
[ Groaning ]

384
00:30:56.905 --> 00:30:59.407
DON'T LET GO !

385
00:31:11.419 --> 00:31:15.924
-[ Footsteps Running ]
- [ Cars Honking ]

386
00:31:16.424 --> 00:31:18.426
[ Gasping ]

387
00:31:18.426 --> 00:31:21.713
[ Man ]
A WITNESS TOOK THIS PHOTOGRAPH
OF ONE OF THE SUSPECTS.

388
00:31:21.713 --> 00:31:26.217
HE MATCHES THE DESCRIPTION
OF A SMALL-TIME BEIJING HOOD.

389
00:31:26.217 --> 00:31:31.339
YOU BETTER GET UP THERE
AND ASK SOME QUESTIONS.

390
00:31:31.339 --> 00:31:36.344
YOU'LL NEED
TO SEE A CAPTAIN PHAT
IN BEIJING ANTICRIME.

391
00:31:40.848 --> 00:31:46.854
HEY. WHAT'S WRONG ?
COME ON. TELL ME.
SOMETHING'S WRONG. ISN'T IT ?

392
00:31:47.855 --> 00:31:49.857
[ Man ]
YEAH. THAT'S THE MAN
WHO ESCAPED.

393
00:31:49.857 --> 00:31:53.861
WHEN WAS THAT ?
FRIDAY.
WHY ?

394
00:31:53.861 --> 00:31:55.863
MY INVESTIGATION.

395
00:31:57.865 --> 00:32:00.868
HE HAS A FAMILY
HERE IN BEIJING.
ISN'T THAT RIGHT ?

396
00:32:01.369 --> 00:32:05.373
THAT'S WHAT I HEAR.
HIS BACKGROUND
IS PRETTY SKETCHY.

397
00:32:05.373 --> 00:32:07.375
COULD I HAVE A LOOK
AT HIS FILE ?

398
00:32:07.375 --> 00:32:09.877
I DON'T HAVE ONE
FOR YOU TO LOOK AT.

399
00:32:09.877 --> 00:32:14.015
I SEE.  THANK YOU.
YOU'VE BEEN VERY HELPFUL.

400
00:32:16.017 --> 00:32:19.520
MY MOM SAYS SHE CAN ONLY
GIVE YOU $55 FOR THE WATCH.

401
00:32:19.520 --> 00:32:22.774
NOT 65.
LIKE YOU ASKED FOR.
WHAT'S THAT ?

402
00:32:22.774 --> 00:32:26.027
BUGS IN A JAR.
WHAT ABOUT IT ?
JOHNNY.

403
00:32:26.027 --> 00:32:29.530
- WELL. I FEEL
  LIKE STOMPING SOME ANTS.
-[ Bully's Pals Laughing ]

404
00:32:29.530 --> 00:32:33.034
[ Boy ]
WAY TO GO. BULL.  HE'S TRYING
TO STARE YOU DOWN. BULL.

405
00:32:35.536 --> 00:32:39.040
JOHNNY. COME ON.
YOU WANT TROUBLE.
ANT BOY ?

406
00:32:41.042 --> 00:32:43.544
HEY. GIVE ME THAT.
[ Bull ]
WHOA. WHAT'S THIS ?

407
00:32:43.544 --> 00:32:45.546
[ Johnny Grunting ]
HEY. LOOK !  ANT BOY'S
DADDY'S A CRIMINAL !

408
00:32:46.047 --> 00:32:47.915
I'LL KILL YOU ALL !
HE'S WANTED
BY THE COPS !

409
00:32:47.915 --> 00:32:49.917
[ Freddy ]
GIVE THAT BACK.

410
00:32:49.917 --> 00:32:52.420
LOOK RIGHT THERE.
THAT'S HIS PICTURE. LOOK !

411
00:32:52.420 --> 00:32:55.423
[ Boys Chanting ]
MOST WANTED !
MOST WANTED !  MOST WANTED !

412
00:32:55.423 --> 00:32:58.426
MOST WANTED !
 MOST WANTED !  MOST WANTED !

413
00:32:58.926 --> 00:33:03.431
[ Boys Continue
  Chanting ]

414
00:33:03.431 --> 00:33:05.433
[ Boy ]
YOUR DAD'S A CRIMINAL.
[ Chanting Continues ]

415
00:33:05.933 --> 00:33:08.569
STOP IT !  ALL OF YOU !
GIVE ME THAT !

416
00:33:08.569 --> 00:33:12.573
GIVE IT !
LEAVE HIM ALONE. YOU CREEPS !

417
00:33:15.576 --> 00:33:18.579
GET HIM !
PICK UP SOME ROCKS. BOYS !

418
00:33:18.579 --> 00:33:22.083
- OUCH !
- [ Boys Laughing ]

419
00:33:22.083 --> 00:33:24.836
[ Bull ]
GET HIM !
OUCH.  OUCH.

420
00:33:24.836 --> 00:33:27.839
[ Man ]
HEY. WHAT'S GOING ON HERE ?

421
00:33:27.839 --> 00:33:30.842
BACK TO YOUR CLASSROOMS.
ALL OF YOU.

422
00:33:30.842 --> 00:33:36.347
HEY. JOHN KUNG.
YOU HAVE A PHONE CALL.
MY OFFICE.

423
00:33:39.350 --> 00:33:41.853
HELLO ?
[ Wei ]
JOHNNY. IT'S ME.

424
00:33:41.853 --> 00:33:45.356
PAPA. WHERE ARE YOU ?

425
00:33:45.356 --> 00:33:47.358
WAIT.
IS ANYBODY THERE ?

426
00:33:47.358 --> 00:33:52.730
YEAH.
DON'T SAY ANYTHING.

427
00:33:52.730 --> 00:33:56.234
WE'RE HERE IN HONG KONG.
WHAT'S HAPPENING WITH MA ?

428
00:33:56.234 --> 00:33:59.737
UM... SHE'S NOT
MOVING AROUND MUCH.

429
00:34:00.238 --> 00:34:02.240
CAN YOU SEND US
SOME MORE MONEY ?

430
00:34:02.240 --> 00:34:04.242
MOM NEEDS MEDICINE.

431
00:34:06.744 --> 00:34:09.747
MORE MONEY IS ON THE WAY.

432
00:34:10.248 --> 00:34:12.250
BUT ABOUT MY PHONE CALL--

433
00:34:12.250 --> 00:34:14.252
BETTER NOT TELL HER.

434
00:34:14.752 --> 00:34:18.756
- HOW ABOUT IF SHE ASKS ?
- PLEASE.

435
00:34:18.756 --> 00:34:22.760
POP. PEOPLE ARE MAKING FUN
OF ME AT SCHOOL.

436
00:34:22.760 --> 00:34:25.263
ABOUT ME ?
YEAH.

437
00:34:25.263 --> 00:34:28.766
WHEN I SEE YOU.
I WILL EXPLAIN THIS STUFF.

438
00:34:31.769 --> 00:34:34.772
WHAT HAPPENS IF MOM...
DOESN'T GET BETTER ?

439
00:34:34.772 --> 00:34:37.775
CALL ME ON MY PAGER.

440
00:34:37.775 --> 00:34:43.281
ONE. ONE.
SEVEN. SEVEN. ONE. THREE.
ONE. NINE. ONE. ZERO.

441
00:34:43.281 --> 00:34:47.285
LEAVE A MESSAGE.
AND I'LL CALL YOU
AS SOON AS I CAN.

442
00:34:48.786 --> 00:34:50.788
JOHNNY. TAKE CARE.

443
00:34:50.788 --> 00:34:53.791
I WILL.  BYE.

444
00:34:53.791 --> 00:34:56.294
SEE YOU.

445
00:34:56.294 --> 00:34:58.296
[ Hangs Receiver Up ]

446
00:35:01.299 --> 00:35:03.301
[ Spits ]

447
00:35:03.801 --> 00:35:05.803
- [ Laughing ]
- STOP IT. YOU GUYS.

448
00:35:05.803 --> 00:35:09.807
PLEASE STOP IT.
FREDDY. ARE YOU OKAY ?

449
00:35:09.807 --> 00:35:15.313
[ Boy Taunting ]
WIPE THE TEARS !
MOST OF THE ANTS ARE GONE.

450
00:35:15.313 --> 00:35:18.816
[ Boys Continue Laughing.
  Taunting ]

451
00:35:19.317 --> 00:35:21.819
[ Bull ]
WHAT ARE YOU LOOKING AT ?

452
00:35:21.819 --> 00:35:23.821
I'LL STOMP BOTH OF YOU TOO !

453
00:35:23.821 --> 00:35:26.824
GET THEM !
[ Yelling ]

454
00:35:43.224 --> 00:35:44.725
NEXT !

455
00:35:46.727 --> 00:35:50.731
[ Groaning ]
WHAT DID YOU DO TO MY ANTS ?

456
00:35:50.731 --> 00:35:52.733
[ Yelling ]

457
00:36:02.109 --> 00:36:06.614
[ Groaning ]
YOU WANT TO SAY SOMETHING BAD
ABOUT MY FATHER ?

458
00:36:06.614 --> 00:36:08.616
[ Bell Ringing ]

459
00:36:08.616 --> 00:36:11.619
[ Groaning ]
GO !

460
00:36:13.120 --> 00:36:16.624
[ Bell Continues Ringing ]
HEY. BUDDY. LET'S GO.

461
00:36:20.011 --> 00:36:24.015
THESE ARE DUE
AT THE END OF THE WEEK.
SPELLING ON MONDAY.

462
00:36:24.015 --> 00:36:27.518
[ Ringing ]

463
00:36:31.022 --> 00:36:34.525
MY MOM'S
TAKING ME SHOPPING.
OKAY.  BYE.

464
00:36:52.543 --> 00:36:58.549
[ Vendors. Customers
  Chattering ]

465
00:36:58.549 --> 00:37:02.553
[ Chattering Continues ]

466
00:37:23.574 --> 00:37:28.579
[ Gasping ]

467
00:37:28.579 --> 00:37:30.581
THIS KID'S A HIKER.

468
00:37:30.581 --> 00:37:32.583
EXCUSE ME.

469
00:37:42.093 --> 00:37:45.596
MA !  HOW ARE YOU FEELING ?

470
00:37:45.596 --> 00:37:48.599
OH. GOOD.
YOU'RE HERE.

471
00:37:48.599 --> 00:37:51.102
I GOT SOME
NEW ANTS TODAY.

472
00:37:51.102 --> 00:37:54.605
LET ME SEE THEM.
HERE.
LOOK AT HOW MANY I GOT.

473
00:37:54.605 --> 00:37:57.108
UH-HUH.
[ Fong ]
EXCUSE ME.

474
00:37:57.108 --> 00:38:00.611
I'M ANNA FONG.
I'VE COME HERE
FROM HONG KONG TODAY.

475
00:38:01.112 --> 00:38:04.615
I WONDER IF I MIGHT
HAVE A WORD ?
JOHNNY. SEE IF THE SOUP IS HOT.

476
00:38:04.615 --> 00:38:06.617
OKAY.

477
00:38:08.619 --> 00:38:11.122
PLEASE SIT DOWN.

478
00:38:11.122 --> 00:38:16.627
JOHNNY.
I BROUGHT YOU
SOME BACON.
THANKS.

479
00:38:16.627 --> 00:38:20.131
WHO'S THAT ?
I DON'T KNOW.

480
00:38:20.131 --> 00:38:22.633
SEE YOU LATER.
BYE.

481
00:38:23.134 --> 00:38:27.638
SO. I WANT TO TALK TO YOU
ABOUT YOUR HUSBAND.
MM-HMM.

482
00:38:27.638 --> 00:38:29.640
HAVE YOU HEARD
FROM KUNG WEI ?

483
00:38:29.640 --> 00:38:32.143
NOT MUCH. REALLY.

484
00:38:32.643 --> 00:38:34.645
DO YOU KNOW HIM ?

485
00:38:34.645 --> 00:38:39.650
GOSH !  I'M SO SURPRISED
HE DIDN'T TELL YOU ABOUT ME.

486
00:38:39.650 --> 00:38:42.153
WE RUN A BUSINESS TOGETHER.

487
00:38:42.153 --> 00:38:47.158
HMM.
IS THE AIRPORT VERY BUSY ?
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT ?

488
00:38:47.658 --> 00:38:50.661
THE AIRPORT.
THE AIRPORT.

489
00:38:50.661 --> 00:38:54.165
OH !  OH. YES. IT WAS.
IT WAS SO CROWDED.

490
00:38:54.165 --> 00:38:57.668
MOM. HERE'S YOUR SOUP.
IT'S HOT.
THANKS.

491
00:39:02.673 --> 00:39:05.176
[ Gags ]

492
00:39:07.678 --> 00:39:11.182
BAD TASTING. BUT IT DOES
HELP ME TO BREATHE.

493
00:39:13.684 --> 00:39:16.687
PAPA SENT US A LETTER.
DO YOU WANT ME TO READ IT ?

494
00:39:16.687 --> 00:39:19.190
YES.
"DEAR JOHNNY.

495
00:39:19.190 --> 00:39:22.693
"FOR AT LEAST ANOTHER WEEK
 I'LL BE IN HONG KONG.

496
00:39:22.693 --> 00:39:27.698
"PLEASE BE AS HELPFUL
 TO YOUR MA AS YOU CAN.

497
00:39:27.698 --> 00:39:29.700
"WHEN WE SEE EACH OTHER.

498
00:39:29.700 --> 00:39:33.704
"YOU CAN BE SURE THAT I WILL
 EXPLAIN EVERYTHING TO YOU.

499
00:39:33.704 --> 00:39:37.708
"MEANWHILE. KEEP ON DOING
 WHAT YOU'RE DOING.

500
00:39:38.209 --> 00:39:41.212
"AND DON'T LISTEN TO WHAT
 PEOPLE MIGHT SAY ABOUT ME.

501
00:39:41.212 --> 00:39:43.714
"I'LL BE HOME
 AS SOON AS I CAN.

502
00:39:43.714 --> 00:39:47.218
"SO TRY AND TAKE CARE
 OF THINGS WHILE I'M GONE.

503
00:39:47.218 --> 00:39:50.721
"IN THE ENVELOPE
 YOU WILL FIND $65--

504
00:39:55.726 --> 00:40:00.731
"I MEAN $55 TO HELP YOU
 PAY FOR MOM'S MEDICINE.

505
00:40:01.232 --> 00:40:03.734
SEE YOU SOON.
LOVE. PAPA."

506
00:40:07.238 --> 00:40:10.741
HERE'S THE $55.
I WANT TO KEEP THE LETTER.
OKAY.

507
00:40:11.242 --> 00:40:14.245
[ Chuckling ]

508
00:40:14.245 --> 00:40:17.248
THAT WAS SO GREAT.

509
00:40:18.749 --> 00:40:21.752
UH... YOUR PAPA
GAVE YOU THIS.

510
00:40:21.752 --> 00:40:26.757
JOHNNY. MISS FONG
IS PAPA'S FRIEND.

511
00:40:26.757 --> 00:40:29.260
SHE. UH--
 SHE WORKS WITH PAPA.

512
00:40:29.260 --> 00:40:33.264
- SHE. UH--  SHE--
- WE BUY AND SELL STOCKS.

513
00:41:11.302 --> 00:41:13.804
[ Wei ]
DEAR JOHNNY.

514
00:41:13.804 --> 00:41:17.808
I KNOW IT MUST SEEM LIKE
I'M ALWAYS WRITING TO YOU
FROM SOME FARAWAY PLACE.

515
00:41:18.309 --> 00:41:20.811
BUT. HOPEFULLY.
THINGS WILL CHANGE SOON.

516
00:41:20.811 --> 00:41:23.814
I'M HOPING TO BE WITH YOU
FOR THE NEW YEAR CELEBRATION.

517
00:41:23.814 --> 00:41:26.317
REMEMBER
TO TAKE CARE OF YOUR MOM.

518
00:41:26.817 --> 00:41:29.820
WHEN I'M NOT THERE.
YOU'RE THE MAN OF THE HOUSE.

519
00:41:40.331 --> 00:41:44.335
- IT'S HIM.
-[ Coughing ]

520
00:41:45.836 --> 00:41:48.839
I'M SO SORRY IF I WOKE YOU.

521
00:41:50.841 --> 00:41:53.344
IT'S OKAY.
I WASN'T SLEEPING.

522
00:41:53.844 --> 00:41:56.847
I KNOW YOU AND KUNG WEI
DON'T WORK TOGETHER.

523
00:41:56.847 --> 00:42:00.851
YOU'RE WITH THE POLICE...
IN HONG KONG.

524
00:42:04.855 --> 00:42:08.859
HOW MUCH TROUBLE
IS WEI IN ?

525
00:42:10.361 --> 00:42:13.364
UH... IT'S NOTHING.
REALLY.

526
00:42:13.364 --> 00:42:17.368
I APPRECIATE YOU
MAKING IT SO EASY ON US.

527
00:42:17.868 --> 00:42:22.873
I DON'T KNOW WHAT HE DOES.
BUT I'M SURE IT ISN'T GOOD.

528
00:42:22.873 --> 00:42:24.875
AND...

529
00:42:24.875 --> 00:42:28.379
I CAN TELL YOU THAT...

530
00:42:28.379 --> 00:42:31.382
HE'S A WONDERFUL FATHER...

531
00:42:31.882 --> 00:42:36.387
AND A GOOD HUSBAND TOO.

532
00:42:36.387 --> 00:42:39.390
IT'S HARD TO BELIEVE
ALL THE BAD THINGS I HEAR.

533
00:42:39.390 --> 00:42:43.394
HE WORRIES SO MUCH.

534
00:42:43.394 --> 00:42:45.896
IT'S HARD TO BELIEVE...

535
00:42:45.896 --> 00:42:49.900
THAT HE COULD DO
WHAT THEY SAY HE DOES.

536
00:42:52.403 --> 00:42:56.407
[ Sighs. Sobs ]

537
00:42:56.407 --> 00:43:01.412
[ Coughing ]

538
00:43:01.412 --> 00:43:03.914
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT ?

539
00:43:05.416 --> 00:43:08.419
YOU WON'T FIND ANYTHING.

540
00:43:08.419 --> 00:43:10.921
HE ALWAYS DISAPPEARS...

541
00:43:10.921 --> 00:43:13.924
AND THEN ONE DAY
HE JUST SHOWS UP.

542
00:43:13.924 --> 00:43:16.927
YOU'RE SO TRUSTING.
I'M NOT SURE WHAT TO DO.

543
00:43:16.927 --> 00:43:20.431
[ Sighs ]
WHAT I'D LIKE YOU TO DO...

544
00:43:20.431 --> 00:43:22.933
IS TO TAKE BACK
YOUR MONEY.

545
00:43:24.435 --> 00:43:26.937
TAKE IT NOW.

546
00:43:28.939 --> 00:43:33.444
MY JOHNNY--
HE'S GOING TO NEED SOMEONE...

547
00:43:33.444 --> 00:43:37.948
WHOSE COMPASSION MATTERS--

548
00:43:38.449 --> 00:43:40.951
MATTERS MORE TO HER
THAN HER DUTY.

549
00:43:40.951 --> 00:43:45.456
PLEASE HELP.
PROMISE ME.

550
00:43:51.612 --> 00:43:56.116
[ Chattering ]

551
00:43:56.116 --> 00:43:59.119
[ Freddy ]
JOHNNY. CAN YOU HANG OUT
WITH ME TODAY ?

552
00:43:59.119 --> 00:44:01.622
NO. GOTTA HELP MY MOM.

553
00:44:01.622 --> 00:44:04.625
TOO BAD.
SEE YOU LATER.  BYE.

554
00:44:12.883 --> 00:44:15.386
GOOD MORNING.

555
00:44:15.386 --> 00:44:18.889
WOW. YOU'RE WEARING
MY MAMA'S DRESS.

556
00:44:18.889 --> 00:44:21.892
IT LOOKS GOOD ON YOU.
ANNA.
OH. REALLY ?

557
00:44:21.892 --> 00:44:27.398
REALLY.  I'M ALWAYS SURPRISED
BY THE CLOTHES SOME WOMEN
PICK OUT TO WEAR.

558
00:44:28.899 --> 00:44:31.402
SO. JOHNNY. YOU'RE ONLY
TEN YEARS OLD.

559
00:44:31.402 --> 00:44:33.404
ALREADY A LADIES' MAN ?

560
00:44:33.404 --> 00:44:35.906
I KNOW WHO'S PRETTY.

561
00:44:35.906 --> 00:44:39.660
MY MOM IS SOMETIMES.

562
00:44:39.660 --> 00:44:41.662
AM I PRETTY ?

563
00:44:42.162 --> 00:44:45.666
FREDDY--
HE TOLD ME HE DIDN'T
THINK YOU WERE PRETTY.

564
00:44:45.666 --> 00:44:47.668
WHAT ?

565
00:44:47.668 --> 00:44:49.670
BUT I TOLD HIM YOU WERE.

566
00:44:50.170 --> 00:44:52.172
AND YOUR TASTE IN WOMEN
IS EXCELLENT.

567
00:44:53.674 --> 00:44:56.176
LET ME ASK YOU SOMETHING.

568
00:44:56.176 --> 00:44:59.680
ARE YOU REALLY
MY PAPA'S FRIEND ?

569
00:45:00.180 --> 00:45:02.683
UH... I--

570
00:45:02.683 --> 00:45:07.688
SEE. MY MAMA SAID
THAT PAPA DOESN'T KNOW
ANYBODY IN HONG KONG.

571
00:45:07.688 --> 00:45:11.191
REALLY ?
AREN'T YOU CLEVER.

572
00:45:11.191 --> 00:45:13.694
WELL. WHAT DOES
YOUR PAPA SAY ?

573
00:45:13.694 --> 00:45:19.199
HE SAYS THAT WHEN
A MAN TALKS. A WOMAN'S
SUPPOSED TO PAY ATTENTION.

574
00:45:20.701 --> 00:45:22.703
IS THAT RIGHT ?

575
00:45:23.203 --> 00:45:27.708
YOUR PAPA TOLD ME THAT
YOU ARE MAN OF THE HOUSE
WHILE HE'S AWAY.

576
00:45:27.708 --> 00:45:30.711
YOU KNOW WHAT HE SHOWED ME ?
A PHOTO OF YOUR FAMILY.

577
00:45:31.211 --> 00:45:33.213
WHAT KIND OF PHOTO ?

578
00:45:33.714 --> 00:45:36.216
A PICTURE OF ALL OF YOU.

579
00:45:38.719 --> 00:45:42.372
[ Laughing ]

580
00:45:48.629 --> 00:45:52.132
HERE.
I'LL OWE IT TO YOU.
ALL RIGHT ?

581
00:45:52.132 --> 00:45:56.136
DON'T YOU WORRY ABOUT IT.
EASY COME. EASY GO.  HUH ?

582
00:45:56.136 --> 00:45:58.639
PRETTY SOON WE'LL BOTH
BE ROLLING IN IT.

583
00:46:00.641 --> 00:46:02.643
HEY. TWO BURGERS.

584
00:46:03.143 --> 00:46:04.645
OKAY.

585
00:46:07.147 --> 00:46:10.150
THERE'S A BIG JOB COMING UP.
THAT'S WHAT I HEAR.

586
00:46:10.150 --> 00:46:12.152
SURE THERE'S A BIG JOB.

587
00:46:12.152 --> 00:46:15.155
ANTIQUES FROM
THE CHINESE MAINLAND.

588
00:46:15.155 --> 00:46:17.658
ANTIQUES ?
FOR WHO ?

589
00:46:17.658 --> 00:46:20.160
A DEALER.
SOME BROAD NAMED LI.

590
00:46:20.160 --> 00:46:25.165
SO MY BUYERS ARE VERY PLEASED
WITH THE ANTIQUE SAMPLES
YOU'VE SMUGGLED OUT.

591
00:46:25.666 --> 00:46:29.169
I'VE SET UP THE AUCTION
FOR LATE SUNDAY AFTERNOON.

592
00:46:29.169 --> 00:46:31.171
HAVE YOU THOUGHT
ABOUT THE COPS ?

593
00:46:31.171 --> 00:46:36.176
YES. WE'VE TAKEN CARE
OF THAT SITUATION.

594
00:46:36.176 --> 00:46:38.679
YOU SEE.
SUNDAY'S AUCTION...

595
00:46:39.179 --> 00:46:42.182
WILL TAKE PLACE
ON A PRIVATE BOAT.

596
00:46:42.182 --> 00:46:46.687
I'D SAY OUR GUESTS WILL BE
CARRYING MILLIONS IN CASH.

597
00:46:46.687 --> 00:46:48.689
THAT MODIFIES THE WHOLE PLAN.

598
00:46:49.189 --> 00:46:53.193
HOW ?  YOU'RE NOT SUGGESTING
THAT WE ROB THEM ?

599
00:46:53.694 --> 00:46:57.197
I'M NOT SUGGEST--
D-DO YOU THINK THAT'S
WHAT I'M SUGGESTING ?

600
00:46:57.197 --> 00:46:59.700
IT'S NOT SUCH A BAD IDEA.

601
00:46:59.700 --> 00:47:03.203
OF COURSE. WE'D HAVE TO KILL
ALL OF THEM AND BURN THE SHIP...

602
00:47:03.203 --> 00:47:05.706
TO GET RID
OF THE EVIDENCE.

603
00:47:05.706 --> 00:47:10.210
AH. YES. I LIKE IT.

604
00:47:10.210 --> 00:47:13.213
BEATS HOCKING
HOT ANTIQUES.
BUT WATCH OUT.

605
00:47:13.213 --> 00:47:15.215
I HEAR THAT
BEIJING ANTICRIME
IS LOOKING...

606
00:47:15.215 --> 00:47:17.718
TO INFILTRATE
YOUR CREW.
WHO SAYS ?

607
00:47:17.718 --> 00:47:20.220
IT'S THE WORD
ON THE STREET. BABY.

608
00:47:20.220 --> 00:47:24.224
[ Li Laughing ]

609
00:47:24.224 --> 00:47:29.229
[ Bo ]
I TAKE HALF OFF THE TOP.
AND YOU GUYS SPLIT THE REST.

610
00:47:29.730 --> 00:47:34.234
THINK YOU CAN DIVIDE
A MILLION SIX WAYS ?

611
00:47:34.234 --> 00:47:37.738
I CAN.
IT'S A LOT OF MONEY.

612
00:47:38.238 --> 00:47:40.240
THESE LOOK LIKE
THEY COME FROM XI'AN.

613
00:47:40.240 --> 00:47:45.245
JUST LOOK AT THE SIZE
OF THE HORSE'S HEAD
IN PROPORTION TO ITS BODY.

614
00:47:45.245 --> 00:47:47.748
THERE'S NO MISTAKING IT.

615
00:47:49.249 --> 00:47:51.251
STRANGE ONE.
AREN'T YOU ?

616
00:47:51.251 --> 00:47:53.754
HOW WOULD YOU KNOW
WHERE THIS STUFF COMES FROM ?

617
00:47:53.754 --> 00:47:56.123
I'VE BEEN AROUND A BIT.

618
00:47:56.123 --> 00:47:58.125
[ Bo ]
I LIKE THAT.

619
00:47:58.125 --> 00:48:00.127
IN ORDER FOR YOU
TO MOVE THIS.

620
00:48:00.127 --> 00:48:04.631
THE MAN IN CHARGE MUST
HAVE SOME REAL POWER.

621
00:48:04.631 --> 00:48:06.633
IT'S NOT REALLY A MAN.

622
00:48:06.633 --> 00:48:09.136
MORE LIKE A THING.
[ Laughs ]

623
00:48:09.136 --> 00:48:13.140
[ Continues Laughing ]

624
00:48:14.141 --> 00:48:16.643
CAPTAIN. IT'S ME.

625
00:48:16.643 --> 00:48:19.646
[ Women Laughing ]

626
00:48:19.646 --> 00:48:24.151
LISTEN. THERE ARE STOLEN
ANTIQUES HERE WORTH A FORTUNE
AND A WOMAN NAMED LI--

627
00:48:24.651 --> 00:48:27.654
THAT'S GOOD.
KEEP DIGGING
AND CALL ME BACK.

628
00:48:27.654 --> 00:48:31.658
YEAH. WELL. LISTEN.
HOW MUCH LONGER ARE YOU GONNA
KEEP ME HERE LIKE THIS ?

629
00:48:31.658 --> 00:48:35.162
AS LONG AS IT TAKES.
WE NEED THESE PEOPLE
PUT AWAY.

630
00:48:35.162 --> 00:48:37.164
UNDERSTAND ?
[ Sighs ]

631
00:48:37.164 --> 00:48:39.166
MM-HMM.

632
00:48:43.420 --> 00:48:46.924
[ Johnny ]
DEAR PAPA. HOW ARE YOU ?

633
00:48:46.924 --> 00:48:49.559
I HOPE THAT
YOU'RE GETTING MY LETTERS.

634
00:48:49.559 --> 00:48:54.064
I AM FINE. BUT MAMA
ISN'T GETTING ANY BETTER.

635
00:49:08.946 --> 00:49:11.698
[ Sighs ]
[ Loud Thud ]

636
00:49:11.698 --> 00:49:14.201
[ Crying. Coughing ]

637
00:49:14.201 --> 00:49:18.205
MAMA. ARE YOU ALL RIGHT ?
 MAMA. WAKE UP !  MAMA !

638
00:49:18.205 --> 00:49:20.207
[ Gasping ]
WHAT IS IT.
JOHNNY ?

639
00:49:20.207 --> 00:49:22.709
SHE NEEDS TO GO
TO THE HOSPITAL
RIGHT NOW.

640
00:49:22.709 --> 00:49:25.212
[ Gasping ]

641
00:49:25.212 --> 00:49:29.216
HURRY !  LET'S GO !
ON THE LEFT !
COME ON !  COMING !

642
00:49:29.216 --> 00:49:31.218
IS THERE ANYTHING
I CAN DO ?

643
00:49:31.218 --> 00:49:33.720
MY SON IS JUST TOO YOUNG...

644
00:49:33.720 --> 00:49:36.223
TO UNDERSTAND
ABOUT DYING.

645
00:49:36.223 --> 00:49:39.226
HE NEEDS HIS FATHER.

646
00:49:41.228 --> 00:49:45.732
PLEASE--
 PLEASE FIND WEI.

647
00:49:45.732 --> 00:49:48.235
GIVE HIM THIS LETTER.

648
00:49:50.737 --> 00:49:55.242
IT SAYS...
THAT HE SHOULD TRUST YOU.

649
00:49:55.242 --> 00:49:57.744
AND THAT YOU'LL TRY
TO HELP HIM.

650
00:49:57.744 --> 00:50:01.248
FOR JOHNNY'S SAKE.

651
00:50:01.248 --> 00:50:05.252
WOULD YOU...
DO WHAT YOUR HEART
TELLS YOU IS RIGHT ?

652
00:50:05.252 --> 00:50:10.257
SET YOUR JOB ASIDE.  HELP.

653
00:50:12.759 --> 00:50:16.763
WILL YOU TAKE CARE
OF OUR SON ?

654
00:50:16.763 --> 00:50:19.766
JOHNNY NEEDS YOU.

655
00:50:20.267 --> 00:50:23.770
[ Gasping. Sighs ]

656
00:50:23.770 --> 00:50:27.274
- SALLY !
- [ Groans ]

657
00:50:27.274 --> 00:50:30.277
- DOCTOR !
- MOM !

658
00:50:31.278 --> 00:50:34.781
MOM. YOU'LL BE ALL RIGHT.
TALK TO ME. MAMA.

659
00:50:34.781 --> 00:50:37.784
MAMA ?
[ Weakly ]
JOHNNY...

660
00:50:37.784 --> 00:50:41.288
BETTER LISTEN.

661
00:50:41.288 --> 00:50:45.292
ANNA WILL LOOK AFTER YOU.

662
00:50:48.795 --> 00:50:52.799
SHE'LL TAKE YOU TO PAPA.
[ Wheezing ]

663
00:50:52.799 --> 00:50:55.802
NOW. JOHNNY...

664
00:50:55.802 --> 00:50:58.305
JUST...

665
00:50:58.305 --> 00:51:00.307
PROMISE ME--

666
00:51:00.307 --> 00:51:01.808
PROMISE ME...

667
00:51:02.309 --> 00:51:04.811
[ Crying ]
THAT YOU'LL
ALWAYS REMEMBER...

668
00:51:05.312 --> 00:51:08.315
HOW MUCH I LOVE YOU.

669
00:51:10.317 --> 00:51:13.320
I'LL ALWAYS REMEMBER THAT.

670
00:51:13.320 --> 00:51:16.323
WILL YOU
ALWAYS REMEMBER THAT...

671
00:51:16.323 --> 00:51:19.826
NO MATTER
HOW MUCH TIME PASSES BY...

672
00:51:19.826 --> 00:51:23.330
I WON'T FORGET YOU ?

673
00:51:23.330 --> 00:51:27.334
YES.
GIVE THIS TO MISS FONG.

674
00:51:27.334 --> 00:51:29.836
[ Wheezing ]

675
00:51:29.836 --> 00:51:32.839
SHE'LL GIVE IT TO PAPA.

676
00:51:34.841 --> 00:51:37.344
FIND HIM. ANNA.

677
00:51:37.844 --> 00:51:39.846
I WILL.

678
00:51:39.846 --> 00:51:44.351
WE STARTED TO BE...

679
00:51:44.351 --> 00:51:46.853
SO CLOSE.

680
00:51:46.853 --> 00:51:49.856
PROBABLY...

681
00:51:49.856 --> 00:51:51.858
WE'D BE--

682
00:51:51.858 --> 00:51:55.362
WE'D BE BEST FRIENDS.

683
00:51:55.362 --> 00:51:58.365
I-I HOPE--

684
00:51:58.865 --> 00:52:00.867
I HOPE--

685
00:52:00.867 --> 00:52:03.870
[ Exhales ]

686
00:52:44.544 --> 00:52:48.048
ANNA. I DON'T WANT
TO BE ALL ALONE.

687
00:52:48.048 --> 00:52:52.052
[ Thunderclap ]

688
00:52:57.741 --> 00:53:00.744
[ Pager Beeping ]
HEY. TURN OFF YOUR PAGERS.

689
00:53:00.744 --> 00:53:04.748
IT'S NOT MINE.
I SAID
TURN THEM OFF.

690
00:53:04.748 --> 00:53:07.250
[ Beeping Continues ]
[ Thug ]
WHO IS IT ?

691
00:53:07.751 --> 00:53:10.871
[ Continues Beeping ]

692
00:53:16.509 --> 00:53:18.011
ARE YOU DEAF OR WHAT ?

693
00:53:25.385 --> 00:53:27.387
[ Chuckles ]

694
00:53:30.390 --> 00:53:32.275
HONEST TO GOD ?

695
00:53:33.777 --> 00:53:37.147
- [ Coughing ]
- HEY !

696
00:53:37.530 --> 00:53:39.783
HANDS UP WHERE
WE CAN SEE THEM !

697
00:53:39.783 --> 00:53:43.787
- PLEASE STOP IT !
- YOU BETTER LEARN TO LISTEN
  WHEN I'M TALKIN'.

698
00:53:48.792 --> 00:53:52.295
[ Yelling ]

699
00:53:52.295 --> 00:53:55.298
- [ Continues Yelling ]
- [ Laughing ]

700
00:53:55.298 --> 00:53:57.300
- [ Continues Laughing ]
- [ Continues Yelling ]

701
00:53:59.052 --> 00:54:04.057
- [ Laughing ]
- [ Yelling ]

702
00:54:06.059 --> 00:54:11.064
- [ Grunts. Breathes Deeply ]
- YOU'LL BE HOME SOON.

703
00:54:13.066 --> 00:54:15.068
OH. GOD.

704
00:54:17.570 --> 00:54:21.074
YOU'LL BE SORRY YOU
EVEN THOUGHT ABOUT
MESSING WITH ME !

705
00:54:23.076 --> 00:54:25.078
[ Gasping ]
[ Blows Continue.
  Yelling ]

706
00:54:26.579 --> 00:54:29.082
- [ Groaning ]
- [ Grunting ]

707
00:54:29.082 --> 00:54:32.585
[ Groaning Continues ]
LET ME HAVE A PIECE OF HIM !

708
00:54:32.585 --> 00:54:36.089
[ Groans ]
YOU MESS WITH HIM.
THAT'S WHAT YOU GET !

709
00:54:36.089 --> 00:54:38.091
YOU WANT
SOME MORE. HUH ?

710
00:54:49.602 --> 00:54:52.605
WHAT'S WITH YOU ?
YOU CRAZY OR WHAT ?

711
00:54:53.106 --> 00:54:56.109
BOSS MUST LIKE YOU.

712
00:54:56.109 --> 00:54:58.111
[ Beeping ]
OTHERWISE.
YOU'D BE DEAD.

713
00:54:59.612 --> 00:55:02.615
ANYWAY. LET ME WARN YOU.
FOR YOUR OWN GOOD.

714
00:55:02.615 --> 00:55:05.118
FIGHTING WITH BO
IS A GOOD WAY
TO GET KILLED.

715
00:55:06.619 --> 00:55:09.122
OKAY ?
BO IS A KILLER.

716
00:55:14.194 --> 00:55:17.697
PACK SOME SWEATERS.
IT GETS COLD AT NIGHT
IN HONG KONG.

717
00:55:21.201 --> 00:55:23.703
OH. AND DON'T FORGET
TO BRING SOME BOOKS ALONG
FOR THE TRIP.

718
00:55:23.703 --> 00:55:27.207
ANYTHING BIG
YOU CAN FIT
IN MY SUITCASE.

719
00:55:27.207 --> 00:55:30.210
COME ON.
I'VE GOT PLENTY OF ROOM
RIGHT OVER HERE.

720
00:55:33.713 --> 00:55:36.716
WHAT ARE YOU
LOOKING FOR ?
I DON'T KNOW.

721
00:55:36.716 --> 00:55:39.219
GO ON.  MAKE SURE YOU
HAVEN'T FORGOTTEN ANYTHING.
GO AHEAD.

722
00:55:43.223 --> 00:55:45.725
[ Children Playing ]

723
00:55:45.725 --> 00:55:48.728
JOHNNY. YOU'RE GOING ?

724
00:55:49.229 --> 00:55:50.730
YEAH. I'M GOING.

725
00:55:52.732 --> 00:55:54.734
HERE. TAKE IT.
WHAT'S WRONG ?

726
00:55:54.734 --> 00:55:56.736
IT'S A PRESENT
FOR GOING AWAY.

727
00:55:56.736 --> 00:55:59.239
MY MOM SAID
YOU SHOULD HAVE IT.

728
00:55:59.239 --> 00:56:02.242
COME ON.
TAKE IT.

729
00:56:02.242 --> 00:56:04.744
YOUR DAD GAVE IT TO YOU.
DIDN'T HE ?

730
00:56:04.744 --> 00:56:06.746
IT'S YOURS.

731
00:56:09.749 --> 00:56:11.751
THANK YOU.

732
00:56:24.264 --> 00:56:26.766
WE DON'T KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT THE GUY.

733
00:56:30.270 --> 00:56:32.772
[ Crying ]

734
00:56:32.772 --> 00:56:35.775
[ Crying Continues ]

735
00:56:35.775 --> 00:56:37.777
JOHNNY.

736
00:56:37.777 --> 00:56:40.780
HOW COME SO... FAR ?

737
00:56:40.780 --> 00:56:42.782
[ Continues Crying ]

738
00:56:42.782 --> 00:56:45.285
[ Crying Continues ]

739
00:56:45.785 --> 00:56:47.787
BYE.

740
00:56:48.788 --> 00:56:51.291
BYE. JOHNNY.
HAVE A SAFE TRIP.

741
00:57:04.821 --> 00:57:07.824
[ Man ]
THAT'S IT RIGHT THERE.
THAT'S GOOD.

742
00:57:07.824 --> 00:57:09.826
[ Man #2 ]
NOW IT'S MY TURN.

743
00:57:10.827 --> 00:57:13.079
HEY. DUMMY.

744
00:57:15.582 --> 00:57:17.584
[ Groans ]
DON'T SCARE ME
LIKE THAT !

745
00:57:18.084 --> 00:57:20.587
[ Chattering ]
WE'RE NOT IN HONG KONG.

746
00:57:20.587 --> 00:57:24.090
WHAT'S UP. INSPECTOR ?
CAN YOU TAKE US
TO THE ISLAND ?

747
00:57:24.090 --> 00:57:27.093
WHAT ?
TAKE YOU AND THE KID ?
SHH.

748
00:57:27.093 --> 00:57:31.598
AH. MISS FONG. THIS MUST BE
YOUR SON THEN. RIGHT ?
JUST A MINUTE.

749
00:57:31.598 --> 00:57:36.102
MY POP'S KUNG WEI.
I'M NOT HER SON.
WHAT'S WRONG WITH YOU ?

750
00:57:39.105 --> 00:57:43.109
- WHAT'S THAT ?
- THE INSPECTOR
  HAS GOT A KID WITH HER.

751
00:57:43.109 --> 00:57:45.111
[ Man Over Phone ]
HIS FATHER'S NAME
IS KUNG WEI.

752
00:57:45.111 --> 00:57:49.616
STOP WHAT YOU'RE DOING.
ROUND UP SOME GUYS
AND ROUGH HER UP.

753
00:57:49.616 --> 00:57:53.002
- UNDERSTAND ?
- GOT IT.

754
00:57:53.002 --> 00:57:55.004
[ Sighs ]
WHAT'S UP ?

755
00:57:55.004 --> 00:57:59.509
OH. NOT MUCH.
HOW COME YOU GUYS
ARE SO QUIET ?

756
00:57:59.509 --> 00:58:01.511
LET'S HAVE A ROUND.

757
00:58:02.629 --> 00:58:04.631
LISTEN. DUMMY.
I'M WARNING YOU.

758
00:58:04.631 --> 00:58:07.133
DON'T DOUBLE-CROSS ME.
[ Man Yells ]

759
00:58:09.135 --> 00:58:11.137
[ Yelling ]
[ Groaning ]

760
00:58:13.273 --> 00:58:15.775
[ Grunting ]

761
00:58:17.894 --> 00:58:18.895
[ Yelling ]

762
00:58:20.530 --> 00:58:24.033
ANNA.
THE BIG ONE'S MINE.
YUP.

763
00:58:24.033 --> 00:58:26.536
[ Grunts. Yells ]

764
00:58:26.536 --> 00:58:29.038
[ Thugs Groaning ]

765
00:58:29.038 --> 00:58:32.292
[ Yelling ]

766
00:59:02.188 --> 00:59:04.190
[ Yells ]

767
00:59:13.700 --> 00:59:15.702
[ Anna ]
THE LETTER.

768
00:59:22.208 --> 00:59:24.711
[ Gasps ]
THEY MADE ME DO IT.
GO.

769
00:59:26.212 --> 00:59:28.715
[ Shuddering ]
ANNA.

770
00:59:29.716 --> 00:59:33.219
WILL THEY BE BACK ?
NO.
COME ON.

771
00:59:35.722 --> 00:59:37.724
[ Johnny ]
THAT WAS AWESOME !
TELL THE TRUTH. ANNA.

772
00:59:37.724 --> 00:59:39.726
YOU'RE A COP.
AREN'T YOU ?

773
00:59:39.726 --> 00:59:42.228
YEAH.

774
00:59:42.228 --> 00:59:46.733
LOOK. JOHNNY.
I FIRST CAME
TO ARREST YOUR PAPA.

775
00:59:46.733 --> 00:59:50.236
BUT I CHANGED MY MIND.
WHY ?

776
00:59:50.737 --> 00:59:55.241
I DON'T REALLY BELIEVE THAT
YOUR PAPA'S BROKEN ANY LAWS.

777
00:59:55.241 --> 00:59:59.746
PROBABLY...
HE'S A POLICEMAN.

778
00:59:59.746 --> 01:00:04.250
YEAH.  I CAN'T WAIT
TO TELL THE OTHER KIDS
IN MY SCHOOL.

779
01:00:04.751 --> 01:00:07.754
NO. WE HAVE TO KEEP THIS
OUR LITTLE SECRET.

780
01:00:07.754 --> 01:00:10.256
YOUR PAPA HAS HIS REASONS.

781
01:00:16.763 --> 01:00:20.300
[ Man #1 ]  THE TRUCK'S READY
TO GET LOADED.
[ Man #2 ]  ON THE DOUBLE !

782
01:00:23.803 --> 01:00:26.806
[ Office Chatter ]

783
01:00:26.806 --> 01:00:29.309
[ Chattering Continues ]

784
01:00:30.810 --> 01:00:33.313
YOU PROMISED ME.
WHAT ?

785
01:00:33.313 --> 01:00:36.316
YOU SAID YOU WOULDN'T
GIVE THE PRESS ANYTHING
ABOUT THE BOY.

786
01:00:36.316 --> 01:00:39.819
I TRUSTED YOU !
WELL. WHAT ABOUT
MY INVESTIGATION ?

787
01:00:39.819 --> 01:00:42.822
WHAT WAS I SUPPOSED TO DO ?
I'M A POLICE SERGEANT.

788
01:00:44.324 --> 01:00:47.827
YOU COULD DO
A LITTLE BIT MORE...
TO HELP ME.

789
01:00:49.329 --> 01:00:52.332
YOU SHOULD SEE
IF YOUR WIFE CAN HELP YOU.
THAT'S MY ADVICE.

790
01:00:54.450 --> 01:00:55.952
[ Ringing ]
HELLO ?

791
01:00:55.952 --> 01:00:59.455
- [ Beeps. Wei Over Phone ]
  JOHNNY.
- YOU GOT MY MESSAGE.

792
01:00:59.455 --> 01:01:00.957
WHAT ARE YOU DOING
IN HONG KONG ?

793
01:01:02.959 --> 01:01:05.595
I'M WITH ANNA FONG.
SHE SAYS SHE KNOWS YOU.

794
01:01:05.595 --> 01:01:09.098
[ Talking. Quietly ]

795
01:01:10.600 --> 01:01:12.602
WHERE WERE YOU ?
BUYING A NEWSPAPER.

796
01:01:12.602 --> 01:01:14.604
LET ME HAVE THE KEYS.
WHAT FOR ?

797
01:01:14.604 --> 01:01:17.607
JUST DO IT.
TRY NOT TO SCRATCH
THE PAINT. DAMN IT.

798
01:01:18.608 --> 01:01:20.610
[ Sighs ]
THIS GUY'S CRAZY.

799
01:01:21.110 --> 01:01:23.112
HEY. HOW ABOUT A DRINK ?

800
01:01:28.618 --> 01:01:31.621
HEY. LEAVE A LITTLE
FOR THE REST OF US. HUH ?
KEEP THEM COMING.

801
01:01:38.244 --> 01:01:40.747
HEY. GIVE ME THAT.
HEY.

802
01:01:42.248 --> 01:01:45.251
UH. EXCUSE ME. BOSS.
GOT TO USE THE CAN.

803
01:01:45.251 --> 01:01:47.253
[ Footsteps Departing.
  Quickly ]

804
01:01:49.255 --> 01:01:53.259
IN OTHER NEWS.
HONG KONG POLICE HAVE
REPORTED A MISSING CHILD.

805
01:01:53.259 --> 01:01:56.262
DETECTIVE JAMES SHU
IS ASKING FOR THE PUBLIC'S
ASSISTANCE...

806
01:01:56.262 --> 01:02:00.266
IN HELPING TO LOCATE A MISSING
TEN-YEAR-OLD BOY BY THE NAME
OF JOHN KUNG.

807
01:02:00.266 --> 01:02:03.770
ANYONE WITH INFORMATION
REGARDING THE WHEREABOUTS
OF THE BOY...

808
01:02:03.770 --> 01:02:05.772
OR HIS FATHER. KUNG WEI.

809
01:02:05.772 --> 01:02:07.774
SHOULD CONTACT
THE POLICE HELP LINE.
SHE TOLD.

810
01:02:07.774 --> 01:02:09.275
A CHILD MATCHING
JOHN'S DESCRIPTION--

811
01:02:11.778 --> 01:02:13.279
[ Sighs ]

812
01:02:13.279 --> 01:02:18.034
[ Men Talking ]

813
01:02:32.548 --> 01:02:36.052
INSPECTOR.
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE ?

814
01:02:36.052 --> 01:02:38.554
DETECTIVE SHU ORDERED IT.

815
01:02:41.557 --> 01:02:44.560
JOHNNY ?

816
01:02:46.562 --> 01:02:48.064
[ Johnny ]
HELLO ?
[ Wei ]
JOHNNY.

817
01:02:54.070 --> 01:02:55.571
[ Woman Over Phone ]
WHAT IS YOUR MESSAGE
FOR MR. KUNG WEI ?

818
01:02:56.072 --> 01:02:58.574
THE MESSAGE IS:
DON'T COME. 
TOO DANGEROUS.

819
01:03:10.586 --> 01:03:12.588
[ Wei Over Machine ]
SO YOU'RE STAYING
WITH THIS WOMAN ANNA ?

820
01:03:12.588 --> 01:03:16.092
[ Johnny Over Machine ]
UH-HUH.  SHE'S BEEN REALLY NICE.
SHE THINKS YOU'RE A COP.

821
01:03:16.092 --> 01:03:18.594
[ Wei ]
WHAT ?
[ Johnny ]
ARE YOU. PAPA ?

822
01:03:18.594 --> 01:03:21.097
DID SHE TELL ANYONE THIS ?
NO.

823
01:03:21.097 --> 01:03:23.099
SHE SAID IT WAS
OUR LITTLE SECRET.

824
01:03:23.099 --> 01:03:25.101
AND THAT YOU HAD A GOOD REASON
FOR DOING WHAT YOU DID.

825
01:03:25.101 --> 01:03:28.604
SHE'S A COP TOO.
AND I BET SHE'S A GOOD ONE.

826
01:03:37.113 --> 01:03:39.115
[ Pager Beeping ]

827
01:03:40.616 --> 01:03:43.619
[ Continues Beeping ]

828
01:03:43.619 --> 01:03:46.122
[ Pager Beeping ]

829
01:03:46.122 --> 01:03:48.624
[ Doorknob Clicks ]

830
01:03:48.624 --> 01:03:51.260
STOP.
WHO ARE YOU ?

831
01:03:57.767 --> 01:04:00.770
I KNOW THOSE EYES.
IT WAS YOU.
WASN'T IT ?

832
01:04:01.270 --> 01:04:04.774
YOU BETRAYED JOHNNY.
NOT ME.
IT WAS SOMEONE ELSE.

833
01:04:04.774 --> 01:04:08.778
HOW ABOUT YOU
TELLING THE TRUTH ?
I NEVER BETRAYED HIM.

834
01:04:18.404 --> 01:04:20.406
WHEN WILLYOUSTART
TELLING THE TRUTH ?

835
01:04:20.406 --> 01:04:22.408
YOUR WIFE DIED
THINKING YOU WERE A FUGITIVE.

836
01:04:22.909 --> 01:04:25.912
I CAN'T.

837
01:04:27.914 --> 01:04:30.416
TELL SOMEONE.
 TELL ME.

838
01:04:30.917 --> 01:04:33.920
WHY ?
WHAT DOES IT MATTER ?

839
01:04:36.923 --> 01:04:38.925
[ Policemen Knocking ]
INSPECTOR. OPEN THE DOOR.

840
01:04:38.925 --> 01:04:42.428
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT ?
INSPECTOR ?
BREAK IT IN.

841
01:04:42.428 --> 01:04:44.931
COME ON.
SEARCH THE OTHER ROOM.
INSPECTOR ?

842
01:04:45.431 --> 01:04:46.933
WHAT HAPPENED ?
NOT IN HERE.

843
01:04:47.433 --> 01:04:49.936
- [ Officer ]  NOTHING HERE.
- [ Officer #2 ]  NOT HERE.

844
01:04:49.936 --> 01:04:53.940
HE GOT OUT THE WINDOW.
 HE JUMPED.  LET'S GO.  COME ON.
RIGHT.

845
01:04:53.940 --> 01:04:56.943
[ Footsteps Departing ]

846
01:05:05.334 --> 01:05:08.337
MY FRIEND...

847
01:05:08.838 --> 01:05:11.841
SHOW THIS TO JOHNNY'S PAPA.

848
01:05:19.348 --> 01:05:22.852
[ Sally ]
MY DARLING WEI. I KNOW
I WON'T BE SEEING YOU AGAIN.

849
01:05:22.852 --> 01:05:26.355
SO I'M WRITING ONE LAST TIME.

850
01:05:26.355 --> 01:05:28.858
MISS FONG IS THERE TO HELP YOU.
SHE GAVE ME HER WORD.

851
01:05:28.858 --> 01:05:30.860
SO PLEASE TRUST HER.
[ Drunken Men Laughing ]

852
01:05:31.360 --> 01:05:33.362
SHE'S BEEN VERY KIND TO ME
AND TO JOHNNY.

853
01:05:34.864 --> 01:05:38.367
ALTHOUGH I HAVE NEVER UNDERSTOOD
WHY YOU DO CERTAIN THINGS.

854
01:05:38.367 --> 01:05:41.370
I'M SURE THAT
YOU MUST HAVE GOOD REASONS.

855
01:05:41.370 --> 01:05:44.240
BUT NOW. MORE THAN EVER.

856
01:05:44.240 --> 01:05:46.742
YOUR SON NEEDS YOU.

857
01:05:46.742 --> 01:05:51.247
SO I'M ASKING YOU TO COME BACK
AND BE WITH HIM.

858
01:05:56.252 --> 01:05:58.137
[ Sighs ]

859
01:06:05.645 --> 01:06:09.148
HELLO.
YOUR PAPA SENT
FOR YOU.  GET IN.

860
01:06:13.653 --> 01:06:16.305
[ Thug ]
FINALLY. IT'S HERE.
YEAH. NICE AND HOT.

861
01:06:16.305 --> 01:06:19.308
GIVE ME MINE.
HERE YOU GO.

862
01:06:19.308 --> 01:06:22.311
SPICY.
MUST BE FOR JOHNNY.

863
01:06:23.562 --> 01:06:25.064
[ Johnny. Softly ]
"CAREFUL.  BAD GUY."

864
01:06:26.065 --> 01:06:29.435
[ Thug ]  GOOD PLACE.
[ Nervous Laugh ]
LOOKS GREAT.

865
01:06:29.435 --> 01:06:32.438
GOOD FOR YOU.

866
01:06:32.438 --> 01:06:34.940
[ Door Opens. Closes ]

867
01:06:36.442 --> 01:06:40.329
HEY. KUNG WEI.

868
01:06:40.329 --> 01:06:43.833
WHERE YOU BEEN ?
COME JOIN US.

869
01:06:43.833 --> 01:06:46.335
[ Thug ]
PASS SOME CHOPSTICKS.
OKAY.

870
01:06:50.706 --> 01:06:53.709
TRY A LITTLE BIT
OF THIS.

871
01:06:53.709 --> 01:06:55.961
HEY. WHO'S THIS ?

872
01:06:57.963 --> 01:06:59.849
THE BOY'S NAME IS KUNG.

873
01:06:59.849 --> 01:07:01.350
HEY. MAYBE HE'S YOUR KID.

874
01:07:01.851 --> 01:07:03.352
ARE WE ALL RELATED ?

875
01:07:03.352 --> 01:07:06.222
LOOK UP KUNG
IN THE PHONE BOOK.

876
01:07:06.222 --> 01:07:09.475
THERE'S A MILLION OF US.
[ Chuckling ]

877
01:07:09.475 --> 01:07:12.111
THEY CAN'T ALL BE MINE.

878
01:07:12.111 --> 01:07:13.612
[ Thug ]  WANT SOME MORE ?
YEAH.

879
01:07:14.113 --> 01:07:17.867
[ Thug ]  SURE.
HOW ABOUT A LIGHT ?

880
01:07:17.867 --> 01:07:19.869
[ Bo ]
HEY. KID.
WHAT DOES YOUR DAD DO ?

881
01:07:19.869 --> 01:07:23.372
IS HE A POLICEMAN ?
NONE OF YOUR BUSINESS.

882
01:07:23.372 --> 01:07:27.243
[ Chuckling ]
OH.  WISE GUY.

883
01:07:27.243 --> 01:07:28.744
[ Continues Chuckling ]

884
01:07:29.245 --> 01:07:31.997
YOU BETTER
WATCH YOUR MOUTH !

885
01:07:31.997 --> 01:07:35.000
[ Gasping ]

886
01:07:37.503 --> 01:07:40.506
[ Bo ]  OKAY. JOHNNY.
LET'S YOU AND ME
HAVE A LITTLE TALK.

887
01:07:42.007 --> 01:07:46.512
HUH ?
WHY'D YOU COME
TO HONG KONG ?

888
01:07:49.014 --> 01:07:51.517
TO SEE PAPA.

889
01:07:52.518 --> 01:07:55.020
REALLY ?

890
01:07:55.020 --> 01:07:59.024
SO WHAT'S YOUR PAPA
GONNA DO ?
[ Johnny ]  HE'S GONNA GET YOU.

891
01:08:00.025 --> 01:08:02.027
HE SAID SO.

892
01:08:02.027 --> 01:08:04.530
AH.

893
01:08:04.530 --> 01:08:06.532
YOU STUPID LITTLE BRAT !

894
01:08:06.532 --> 01:08:10.536
HE'S NOT GONNA GET ANYBODY
'CAUSE HE'S TOO SCARED
TO SHOW HIS FACE.

895
01:08:10.536 --> 01:08:12.538
HE WON'T LET YOU
GET AWAY WITH THIS.

896
01:08:13.038 --> 01:08:15.040
HE'LL FIND YOU
AND BUST YOU OPEN !

897
01:08:15.040 --> 01:08:16.542
GET OVER HERE !

898
01:08:20.045 --> 01:08:25.551
-[ Wei ]  DON'T MOVE !
-[ Johnny Gasping ]

899
01:08:25.551 --> 01:08:28.053
[ Gasping ]

900
01:08:28.053 --> 01:08:30.556
[ Gasping Continues ]

901
01:08:30.556 --> 01:08:32.558
[ Gasping ]

902
01:08:33.058 --> 01:08:36.562
SAY YOUR PRAYERS.
WHAT PRAYERS ?

903
01:08:36.562 --> 01:08:39.064
SEA DRAGON BREATHING.

904
01:08:39.064 --> 01:08:41.066
NO MATTER WHAT...

905
01:08:41.066 --> 01:08:44.570
WHEN YOU MEET UP
WITH MY PAPA.

906
01:08:44.570 --> 01:08:47.573
HE WILL FIX ALL OF YOU
FOR GOOD.

907
01:08:47.573 --> 01:08:49.575
NO MATTER WHAT HAPPENS
TO ME.

908
01:08:50.075 --> 01:08:53.078
I KNOW HE'LL FIND YOU.

909
01:08:53.078 --> 01:08:58.083
- [ Gasps. Groans ]
-[ Footsteps Departing ]

910
01:09:00.085 --> 01:09:03.589
MAN. YOU'RE COLD-BLOODED.
I GUESS ALL KUNGS
AREN'T RELATED.

911
01:09:07.593 --> 01:09:10.095
[ Thug ]
HEY. BOSS. WHAT DO WE DO
WITH THE BODY ?

912
01:09:12.097 --> 01:09:15.601
UH. LET'S SEE.
SHOVE IT IN A SACK.

913
01:09:18.604 --> 01:09:21.607
[ Car Engine Starts ]

914
01:09:21.607 --> 01:09:25.611
[ Door Alarm Beeping.
   Door Closes. Beeping Stops ]

915
01:09:25.611 --> 01:09:29.615
HEY. DOG.
HOW ABOUT A PARTY ?

916
01:09:29.615 --> 01:09:32.117
THAT SOUNDS GREAT.

917
01:09:32.117 --> 01:09:35.621
WHY DON'T YOU
PICK THE PLACE ?
ALL RIGHT.

918
01:09:49.835 --> 01:09:52.338
HEY. PARK THE CAR.

919
01:09:58.844 --> 01:10:01.847
[ Wei ]
I'LL BE RIGHT THERE.
I LEFT MY JACKET.

920
01:10:04.350 --> 01:10:06.352
[ Car Departs ]

921
01:10:07.353 --> 01:10:08.854
[ Dialing Touch Phone ]

922
01:10:08.854 --> 01:10:11.857
HELLO ?  WHAT ?
[ Answering Machine ]
HI. THIS IS ANNA.

923
01:10:11.857 --> 01:10:14.360
PLEASE LEAVE YOUR MESSAGE
AT THE TONE.

924
01:10:14.360 --> 01:10:18.364
[ Beeps ]
[ Softly ]
MISS FONG. IT'S KUNG WEI.

925
01:10:18.364 --> 01:10:21.367
I NEED YOUR HELP.
YOU HAVE TO SAVE JOHNNY !

926
01:10:21.367 --> 01:10:25.871
HE'S AT BO'S HOUSE.
OUTSIDE IN THE TRASH.
GET THERE !

927
01:10:26.372 --> 01:10:27.373
[ Hangs Up Receiver ]

928
01:10:29.375 --> 01:10:31.377
YOUR JACKET.

929
01:10:32.878 --> 01:10:35.881
THANK YOU.
[ Pats Back ]

930
01:10:40.886 --> 01:10:43.389
[ Thunder Rumbling ]

931
01:10:46.392 --> 01:10:50.396
COME ON. BABE.
THAT WAS SO FUN.
SEE YOU LATER.

932
01:10:50.396 --> 01:10:52.898
LET'S GET A ROOM
AND KEEP PARTYING.
[ Coughing ]

933
01:10:52.898 --> 01:10:56.402
HEY. WHAT'S UP ?
YOU SICK ?
[ Continues Coughing ]

934
01:10:56.902 --> 01:10:59.905
WE'LL TAKE YOU HOME.
NO. IT'S OKAY.
I'LL WALK IT OFF.

935
01:10:59.905 --> 01:11:03.409
SURE. SUIT YOURSELF.
LET'S GO.
[ Continues Coughing ]

936
01:11:03.409 --> 01:11:05.911
[ Coughing ]

937
01:11:05.911 --> 01:11:07.913
[ Continues Coughing ]
[ Car Departing ]

938
01:11:11.417 --> 01:11:13.919
[ Thunder Rumbling ]

939
01:11:31.437 --> 01:11:34.940
JOHNNY.
WHERE ARE YOU ?
I'M HERE !

940
01:11:34.940 --> 01:11:38.444
[ Car Tires Screech.
   Car Door Opens ]

941
01:11:38.444 --> 01:11:42.948
[ Bo ]
I'M REALLY SORRY
TO SEE YOU HERE.

942
01:11:42.948 --> 01:11:46.452
I WAS STARTING TO LIKE YOU.
YOU'RE ALMOST AS CRAZY AS ME.
[ Gate Closes ]

943
01:11:50.956 --> 01:11:54.460
SO. ARE YOU REALLY A COP ?

944
01:11:54.960 --> 01:11:56.962
[ Exhales ]

945
01:11:56.962 --> 01:12:02.468
COME ON.  I WANT
TO HEAR YOU SAY IT
BEFORE I KILL YOU.

946
01:12:02.468 --> 01:12:06.972
JUST SHOOT ME.
IT DOESN'T MATTER NOW.

947
01:12:07.473 --> 01:12:10.476
I DON'T UNDERSTAND
GUYS LIKE YOU.

948
01:12:10.476 --> 01:12:13.479
I COULD'VE MADE YOU
A MILLIONAIRE.  DON'T YOU
REALIZE HOW EASY IT IS ?

949
01:12:14.480 --> 01:12:17.983
HOW WOULD I KNOW ?
I WAS NEVER AROUND MUCH MONEY.

950
01:12:19.985 --> 01:12:21.987
YOU ALMOST HAD YOUR CHANCE.
RIGHT. BOYS ?

951
01:12:23.989 --> 01:12:25.991
[ Thugs Yelling ]

952
01:12:29.495 --> 01:12:31.497
[ Metal Clanging ]

953
01:12:36.502 --> 01:12:39.505
[ Fighting Continues ]
YOU CAN STOP NOW.
I WANT TO DO THE JOB.

954
01:12:39.505 --> 01:12:42.007
DAMN IT. STOP !
[ Cocks Gun ]

955
01:12:42.007 --> 01:12:45.511
[ Metal Clanging.
  Thug Grunting ]

956
01:12:45.511 --> 01:12:47.513
- [ Fires Gun ]
- [ Thug Screams ]

957
01:12:51.016 --> 01:12:55.020
NOW LOOK WHAT YOU'VE DONE.
YOU WOULDN'T LISTEN.
WOULD YOU ?

958
01:12:58.023 --> 01:13:01.026
SO...

959
01:13:01.026 --> 01:13:04.029
KUNG WEI.
ONE OF MY BEST
YOUNG PROTEGEES.

960
01:13:04.029 --> 01:13:06.532
TURNS OUT
TO BE A COP.

961
01:13:07.032 --> 01:13:11.036
NO. WOULDN'T WANT YOU
TO DIE THAT WAY.
[ Uncocks Gun ]

962
01:13:31.557 --> 01:13:34.059
[ Groans. Drops Gun ]

963
01:13:37.062 --> 01:13:38.564
[ Fighting Continues ]

964
01:13:38.564 --> 01:13:40.566
[ Groans ]
[ Yells ]

965
01:13:49.074 --> 01:13:51.577
[ Groans ]

966
01:13:51.577 --> 01:13:55.080
- RUN HIM OVER !
- UH-HUH. OKAY !

967
01:13:57.583 --> 01:14:00.085
[ Tires Squealing ]

968
01:14:04.089 --> 01:14:07.593
[ Truck Approaching ]

969
01:14:08.093 --> 01:14:11.597
-[ Truck Approaching ]
- DIE !  [ Accelerating ]

970
01:14:13.599 --> 01:14:16.101
-[ Truck Approaching. Rapidly ]
- [ Grunting ]

971
01:14:16.101 --> 01:14:19.104
[ Bo ]
WHAT ?  MOVE !

972
01:14:20.105 --> 01:14:23.108
[ Yells. Drops Pipe ]

973
01:14:41.627 --> 01:14:44.630
FOOL !  CAN'T YOU SEE HIM ?
HE'S RIGHT OVER THERE !

974
01:14:56.141 --> 01:14:57.643
[ Grunting ]

975
01:15:03.148 --> 01:15:06.151
[ Grunting ]

976
01:15:11.657 --> 01:15:15.160
[ Bo. Wei Grunting ]

977
01:15:19.665 --> 01:15:21.667
I'M HERE.
HOLD ON !

978
01:15:37.799 --> 01:15:41.303
[ Tires Squealing ]

979
01:16:11.366 --> 01:16:13.368
JOHNNY.
UNCLE GI.

980
01:16:13.368 --> 01:16:16.371
HEY. I BROUGHT YOU SOME TOYS.
LOOK AT THAT.

981
01:16:16.371 --> 01:16:18.874
A WHOLE BAGFUL OF GOODIES.
SEE THERE ?

982
01:16:18.874 --> 01:16:21.376
THANKS.
THERE YOU GO.
JOHNNY.

983
01:16:21.877 --> 01:16:23.879
FEELING BETTER ?
OH. YEAH.

984
01:16:23.879 --> 01:16:24.880
UNCLE GI ?
WHAT'S THE MATTER ?

985
01:16:25.380 --> 01:16:27.382
WHERE'S MY PAPA ?
DON'T WORRY.

986
01:16:27.382 --> 01:16:30.886
I HAVEN'T HEARD FROM HIM. 
BUT HE'S GOT TO BE SOMEPLACE.

987
01:16:30.886 --> 01:16:34.389
WAIT AND SEE.
I'M SURE HE'LL TURN UP SOON.

988
01:16:34.890 --> 01:16:36.391
DON'T WORRY.
NOW YOU SIT TIGHT.

989
01:16:36.892 --> 01:16:39.895
TRY AND FINISH THIS FOR ME.
IT'S YOUR FAVORITE.

990
01:16:39.895 --> 01:16:42.397
HEY. TOUGH GUY.

991
01:16:42.397 --> 01:16:44.900
YOU SEEM TO BE AS STRONG
AS YOUR PAPA IS.

992
01:16:44.900 --> 01:16:47.402
HOW ABOUT SHOWING ME ?
ALL RIGHT.

993
01:16:47.402 --> 01:16:50.405
THAT WAY.
OL' BO WON'T WANT
ANY PART OF ME. DAMN IT.

994
01:16:50.405 --> 01:16:52.908
WHAT DOES "DAMN IT" MEAN ?

995
01:16:53.408 --> 01:16:55.911
[ Stammering ]
OH. YOU DON'T KNOW
WHAT DAMN IT MEANS.

996
01:16:55.911 --> 01:16:58.914
OKAY.  OKAY. YEAH.

997
01:16:59.915 --> 01:17:01.917
SO. JOHNNY.
HOW'S YOUR CHOW MEIN ?

998
01:17:01.917 --> 01:17:04.419
DAMN IT.
OH !

999
01:17:14.429 --> 01:17:18.433
HOW CAN I HELP YOU.
IF YOU WON'T LET ME ?

1000
01:17:25.440 --> 01:17:27.559
[ Bo ]
THERE'S NO GUNS
ALLOWED AT THE AUCTION.

1001
01:17:27.559 --> 01:17:32.698
YOU GUYS WILL ACT
AS SECURITY GUARDS.

1002
01:17:32.698 --> 01:17:37.202
PLANT ALL THE BOMBS BEFORE
ANYONE BOARDS THE SHIP.
[ Thug ]  OKAY.

1003
01:17:37.202 --> 01:17:41.206
WE'RE GOING
TO BE THE ONLY ONES LEAVING
THAT BOAT IN ONE PIECE.

1004
01:17:41.206 --> 01:17:44.076
DRESS FORMALLY.
SO YOU DON'T STAND OUT.

1005
01:17:44.076 --> 01:17:47.579
ANY QUESTIONS ?
UH. NO.  NO. SIR.
NO. SIR.

1006
01:17:47.579 --> 01:17:51.083
GOOD.
4:00. RIGHT HERE.

1007
01:17:51.083 --> 01:17:53.585
HERE ARE YOUR PASSES.

1008
01:17:53.585 --> 01:17:58.090
BO XIANG'S PLACE ?
[ Man ]  NO GOOD.
WE SAW BO. BUT NOT THE KID.

1009
01:17:58.090 --> 01:18:02.094
THAT WORRIES ME.
THE GOOD NEWS IS WE WENT THROUGH
EVERY GARBAGE BAG ON THE ISLAND.

1010
01:18:02.094 --> 01:18:04.596
SOMEBODY
GOT HIM OUT.
KEEP LOOKING.

1011
01:18:04.596 --> 01:18:07.599
[ Disconnects Line ]
I'VE BEEN LOOKING
FOR JOHNNY.  HE'S NOWHERE.

1012
01:18:07.599 --> 01:18:12.104
OH. UH. HE'S
AT THE SQUAD ROOM.
THE SQUAD ROOM ?

1013
01:18:12.604 --> 01:18:15.107
DON'T GET EXCITED.
IT'S FOR THE BEST.

1014
01:18:15.107 --> 01:18:18.610
THIS WAY. AN OFFICER CAN KEEP
AN EYE ON HIM AT ALL TIMES.
[ Doorbell Rings ]

1015
01:18:18.610 --> 01:18:21.113
OH.
[ Sets Receiver On Table ]

1016
01:18:24.116 --> 01:18:26.118
[ Shu ]  YOU'RE NOT
STILL ANGRY. ARE YOU ?
[ Gasps ]

1017
01:18:26.118 --> 01:18:28.620
COME ON.  OPEN IT.

1018
01:18:28.620 --> 01:18:34.126
[ Anna ]  WHAT DO YOU WANT ?
[ Shu ]  YOU. BUT
I'D SETTLE FOR COFFEE.

1019
01:18:46.638 --> 01:18:49.141
UNCLE GI.
HEY. JOHNNY.
HOW YOU DOING ?

1020
01:18:49.141 --> 01:18:52.144
[ Johnny ]
A LOT BETTER.
DID YOU SEE PAPA ?

1021
01:18:52.144 --> 01:18:54.146
NO. BUT WE CAN TRY
TO PAGE HIM.

1022
01:18:54.146 --> 01:18:56.648
HEY. LOOK AT WHAT
YOU'RE WEARING.

1023
01:18:56.648 --> 01:19:00.152
YEAH. LOOK AT ME. JOHN.
SLICK AS A GREASED RAIL.

1024
01:19:00.152 --> 01:19:04.156
BUTTONED-UP AND READY. BOY.
YOU WON'T SEE ME
DRESSED UP A LOT.

1025
01:19:04.156 --> 01:19:07.159
SOMETHING YOU NEED TO DO.
I WANT YOU TO GET
YOUR BAGS TOGETHER.

1026
01:19:07.159 --> 01:19:09.161
'CAUSE WE'RE GOING
SOMEPLACE ELSE.

1027
01:19:09.161 --> 01:19:12.664
[ Gasps ]

1028
01:19:14.666 --> 01:19:18.053
[ Softly ]
HOLY SMOKES !
DO WHAT I TELL YOU !

1029
01:19:18.053 --> 01:19:21.923
GET OVER THE SIDE.
BUT MAKE SURE THAT MAN
DOESN'T SEE YOU.  OKAY ?

1030
01:19:23.925 --> 01:19:26.428
STAY UNDERWATER UNTIL
I TELL YOU TO COME UP.

1031
01:19:26.428 --> 01:19:28.430
[ Chuckling ]
HI.

1032
01:19:32.434 --> 01:19:34.436
WHERE'S THE KID ?

1033
01:19:37.072 --> 01:19:40.075
MUST BE A MISTAKE.

1034
01:19:40.075 --> 01:19:43.445
- [ Panting ]
- NOW THAT DOES IT !

1035
01:19:43.445 --> 01:19:46.948
YOU SEEM TO FORGET WHO I AM.
SO I'M GOING TO HELP YOU
REMEMBER !  [ Groans ]

1036
01:19:46.948 --> 01:19:48.834
YOU OKAY ?

1037
01:19:48.834 --> 01:19:53.338
NO MORE !
YEAH. I SET THE KID FREE.
SO KILL ME !

1038
01:19:53.338 --> 01:19:56.958
I'VE BEEN A DOG ALL MY LIFE.
BUT I'LL DIE LIKE A MAN
MY OWN WAY !

1039
01:19:56.958 --> 01:20:01.963
- I GUESS YOU WILL.
-[ Gunshots. Gi Groans ]

1040
01:20:08.353 --> 01:20:10.856
READY TO GO. BOSS.

1041
01:20:23.235 --> 01:20:25.737
[ Gi. Johnny Gasping ]

1042
01:20:30.742 --> 01:20:34.746
UNCLE.  UNCLE !
[ Gi Gasping ]

1043
01:20:34.746 --> 01:20:38.250
[ Gasping ]
DON'T DIE. GI !

1044
01:20:38.250 --> 01:20:42.254
GI. LET ME SHOW YOU
SOME OF MY TRICKS.  GI--

1045
01:20:42.254 --> 01:20:47.759
[ Gasping ]
I'M JUST TOO STUPID...

1046
01:20:47.759 --> 01:20:52.264
TO BE
LEARNING TRICKS.
NO.

1047
01:20:52.264 --> 01:20:55.767
YOU DON'T BLAME ME
FOR BRINGING YOUR PAPA ALONG...

1048
01:20:56.268 --> 01:20:58.770
DOWN HERE WITH ME.
DO YOU ?

1049
01:20:58.770 --> 01:21:01.273
NO.  NO !

1050
01:21:03.275 --> 01:21:06.778
GIVE THIS CARD
TO YOUR PAPA.

1051
01:21:06.778 --> 01:21:09.281
I WANT YOU TO TELL HIM...

1052
01:21:09.281 --> 01:21:11.783
HE CAN GET INTO THE AUCTION
WITH THIS CARD.

1053
01:21:15.287 --> 01:21:18.039
HE'LL KNOW WHAT TO DO.

1054
01:21:19.040 --> 01:21:23.044
PAGE HIM TO THIS NUMBER.

1055
01:21:27.048 --> 01:21:29.551
[ Gasping. Loudly ]

1056
01:21:30.051 --> 01:21:34.556
UNCLE. DON'T DIE !
WEAR THIS FOR ME !

1057
01:21:34.556 --> 01:21:37.058
IT'S YOUR GOOD LUCK RING.

1058
01:21:37.058 --> 01:21:40.061
YOU'LL BE ALL RIGHT.

1059
01:21:40.061 --> 01:21:42.564
[ Crying ]

1060
01:21:44.065 --> 01:21:45.567
[ Crying Continues ]

1061
01:21:55.076 --> 01:21:57.078
BYE.

1062
01:22:01.082 --> 01:22:05.086
[ Woman Over Phone ]
MAY I TAKE YOUR MESSAGE
FOR MR. KUNG WEI ?

1063
01:22:05.086 --> 01:22:08.089
[ Johnny ]
TELL HIM TO PLEASE
CALL JOHNNY...

1064
01:22:08.089 --> 01:22:10.091
ON GI DOG'S CELL PHONE.

1065
01:22:10.091 --> 01:22:12.844
I'M WAITING
FOR HIS CALL.

1066
01:22:12.844 --> 01:22:15.730
[ Anna ]
AREN'T YOU FINISHED YET ?
[ Pager Beeping ]

1067
01:22:15.730 --> 01:22:18.233
[ Beeping ]
[ Shu ]  WHAT'S YOUR RUSH ?
YOUR PAGER.

1068
01:22:18.233 --> 01:22:20.235
[ Beeping Continues ]
I'LL GET IT.

1069
01:22:20.735 --> 01:22:22.737
[ Beeping Continues ]

1070
01:22:22.737 --> 01:22:26.107
[ Beeping Continues ]
I THOUGHT YOU WANTED
TO TALK TO ME.  I'M READY.

1071
01:22:26.107 --> 01:22:28.610
[ Beeping ]

1072
01:22:28.610 --> 01:22:31.613
[ Dialing ]

1073
01:22:33.615 --> 01:22:36.117
THIS IS FIVE YEARS OVERDUE.

1074
01:22:38.119 --> 01:22:40.622
SEE. I...
FINALLY STARTED TALKING
TO MY WIFE...

1075
01:22:41.122 --> 01:22:43.124
ABOUT A DIVORCE.

1076
01:22:45.126 --> 01:22:47.128
TAKE YOUR TIME.

1077
01:22:47.128 --> 01:22:52.634
[ Chuckling ]

1078
01:22:55.637 --> 01:22:58.640
NO.
BUT WHY ?

1079
01:22:59.140 --> 01:23:03.144
I FOUND OUT THAT
PEOPLE CAN CHANGE.

1080
01:23:10.035 --> 01:23:14.039
MAYBE NEXT TIME
YOU'LL KNOW WHAT'S
IMPORTANT TO YOU.

1081
01:23:37.929 --> 01:23:41.433
[ Wei Over Machine ]  HELLO.
[ Johnny ]  PAPA. BO XIANG'S
GONNA SET UP SOME BOMBS...

1082
01:23:41.433 --> 01:23:44.319
AT THE ART AUCTION
IN THE HARBOR !

1083
01:23:44.319 --> 01:23:47.188
I PUT A PASS FOR YOU
IN THE PHONE BOOTH
AT PAC JAC PIER.

1084
01:23:47.188 --> 01:23:50.075
[ Wei ]
I'M ON MY WAY.
BE CAREFUL.
[ Beeps ]

1085
01:23:53.645 --> 01:23:56.648
[ Bo ]
WHAT'S GOING ON ?

1086
01:23:56.648 --> 01:23:59.150
STUPID THING WON'T WORK !
IT'S A TOTAL WASTE OF TIME !

1087
01:23:59.150 --> 01:24:02.654
I THINK I CAN FIX IT.
IT'S ALL BECAUSE
OF THAT WITCH LI.

1088
01:24:03.154 --> 01:24:06.157
YOU SHOULD HAVE ASKED HER
TO HAVE THIS STUFF
ALREADY SET UP FOR US.

1089
01:24:08.159 --> 01:24:13.665
[ Wincing ]
BOY. COMMENT NUMBER ONE.
MAXIMUM FOR THE DAY.

1090
01:24:13.665 --> 01:24:15.667
WHEN YOU EXCEED
THAT LIMIT. YOU DIE.

1091
01:24:15.667 --> 01:24:19.170
ANY COMMENT ?
WHAT A SURPRISE.
NOT ME.

1092
01:24:20.672 --> 01:24:22.173
[ Thug ]
BOSS. IT'S FIXED.

1093
01:24:24.175 --> 01:24:27.178
ALL RIGHT.
LOOKS LIKE ALL
THE CAMERAS ARE WORKING.

1094
01:24:27.679 --> 01:24:30.181
AND ALL SIX BOMBS
ARE IN PLACE.

1095
01:24:31.182 --> 01:24:34.185
NOW. YOU KEEP AN EYE
ON THE MONITORS.

1096
01:24:34.185 --> 01:24:36.688
IF ANYBODY SPOTS THE BOMBS.
LET US KNOW.

1097
01:24:36.688 --> 01:24:38.690
LET'S GO.

1098
01:24:51.202 --> 01:24:53.705
[ Speedboat Departing ]

1099
01:24:56.207 --> 01:24:58.209
WHAT THE HELL ?

1100
01:25:02.213 --> 01:25:04.716
[ Groans ]

1101
01:25:16.728 --> 01:25:18.730
[ Crowd Chattering ]

1102
01:25:18.730 --> 01:25:20.732
THE BOMBS !

1103
01:25:20.732 --> 01:25:23.735
THAT'S WHERE THEY ARE.

1104
01:25:25.737 --> 01:25:27.739
[ Crowd Chattering ]

1105
01:25:32.360 --> 01:25:38.366
[ Johnny ]
PAPA. LOOK UP AT THE CAMERA.
I CAN SEE YOU FROM BO'S BOAT.

1106
01:25:38.366 --> 01:25:41.870
THERE'S A BOMB BEHIND YOU.
ATTACHED TO THE SIDE
OF THE SHIP.

1107
01:25:48.877 --> 01:25:51.880
[ Passing Crowd Chattering ]

1108
01:26:02.774 --> 01:26:08.279
LOOK UNDERNEATH THE TOP DECK
NEAR THE RAILING.

1109
01:26:20.542 --> 01:26:23.044
THE REST OF THEM
ARE IN THE BOTTOM
OF THE BOAT.

1110
01:26:23.044 --> 01:26:27.549
[ Disconnects Line ]
ISN'T TECHNOLOGY GREAT ?

1111
01:26:27.549 --> 01:26:29.300
[ Men Chattering ]
[ Beeps ]

1112
01:26:29.300 --> 01:26:30.802
[ Chattering Continues ]

1113
01:26:30.802 --> 01:26:34.806
[ Woman ]
AH. WELCOME.
WELCOME ABOARD. SIR.

1114
01:26:35.306 --> 01:26:36.808
AH !
[ Chuckling ]
HEY.

1115
01:26:37.308 --> 01:26:38.810
MR. BO.
MISS LI.

1116
01:26:38.810 --> 01:26:42.313
SO NICE
TO SEE YOU AGAIN. HUH ?
YEAH.

1117
01:26:42.313 --> 01:26:45.817
[ Johnny ]
THE REST OF THEM
ARE IN THE BOTTOM OF THE BOAT.

1118
01:26:59.330 --> 01:27:01.332
HERE. WHY DON'T YOU
EXAMINE IT MORE CLOSELY ?

1119
01:27:10.592 --> 01:27:13.595
THERE ARE TWO MORE BOMBS.
I CAN SEE THEM.

1120
01:27:15.597 --> 01:27:18.099
THERE ARE TWO MORE BOMBS.
I CAN SEE THEM.

1121
01:27:20.101 --> 01:27:22.604
ALMOST THERE NOW.

1122
01:27:22.604 --> 01:27:27.108
WHEN YOU BEND DOWN.
AT YOUR RIGHT FOOT.
YOU WILL SEE IT.

1123
01:27:33.114 --> 01:27:36.117
[ Beeping Rapidly ]

1124
01:27:43.625 --> 01:27:46.127
[ Li ]
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN.
THE AUCTION WILL BEGIN...

1125
01:27:46.127 --> 01:27:49.747
IN JUST A MINUTE.
SO PLEASE GATHER AROUND.

1126
01:27:49.747 --> 01:27:51.249
THE BIDDING WILL BE
IN $5.000 INCREMENTS.

1127
01:27:51.749 --> 01:27:55.253
WE'LL WAIT.
YES. LET'S.

1128
01:27:55.253 --> 01:27:58.756
ITEM NUMBER ONE
IS A TERRA COTTA STATUTE
FROM THE XI'AN--

1129
01:28:00.758 --> 01:28:03.261
[ Continues Dialing ]

1130
01:28:03.261 --> 01:28:05.763
[ Auctioneer ]
DO WE HAVE AN OPENING BID ?
SEVENTY.

1131
01:28:05.763 --> 01:28:07.765
SEVENTY-FIVE.

1132
01:28:07.765 --> 01:28:11.769
SHOULD WE TOP IT ?
 SHOULD WE ?
YES.

1133
01:28:14.772 --> 01:28:17.275
SORRY. POP.
BATTERY'S DEAD.

1134
01:28:17.775 --> 01:28:20.778
IT'S RIGHT HERE.

1135
01:28:20.912 --> 01:28:24.916
[ Auctioneer ]
TWO HUNDRED THOUSAND DOLLARS.
FINAL CALL.

1136
01:28:24.916 --> 01:28:27.919
I'M GOING
TO CLOSE THE BIDDING
AT 200.000 U.S.--

1137
01:28:28.419 --> 01:28:30.421
HOLD IT.

1138
01:28:30.421 --> 01:28:32.540
PUT ALL YOUR CASH
ON THE PODIUM.

1139
01:28:32.540 --> 01:28:36.044
- YOUR MONEY IS MINE.
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN ?

1140
01:28:36.044 --> 01:28:39.547
I'M IN CONTROL OF A SHIP
FULL OF TIME BOMBS.

1141
01:28:39.547 --> 01:28:42.550
LISTEN. BO.
LET'S TALK THIS OVER.
PLEASE CALM DOWN. EVERYONE.

1142
01:28:42.550 --> 01:28:45.553
SO. WHAT'S THERE TO TALK ABOUT ?
[ Auctioneer ]
STAY WHERE YOU ARE.  STAY CALM.

1143
01:28:45.553 --> 01:28:49.057
- LISTEN TO ME RIGHT NOW !
- FIRST. YOU OUGHT
  TO CHECK YOUR POCKET.

1144
01:28:53.811 --> 01:28:56.197
- [ Beeps ]
- [ Crowd Gasps ]

1145
01:28:57.699 --> 01:29:00.201
BYE-BYE.

1146
01:29:00.702 --> 01:29:03.204
NOW. IF YOU DON'T
TAKE OUT YOUR CASH.

1147
01:29:03.705 --> 01:29:05.707
YOU KNOW WHAT HAPPENS.

1148
01:29:06.207 --> 01:29:08.209
SO I SUGGEST
YOU START DOING IT.

1149
01:29:08.209 --> 01:29:14.215
[ Crowd Clamoring ]

1150
01:29:32.233 --> 01:29:34.235
NOT YOU AGAIN ?

1151
01:29:34.235 --> 01:29:37.238
I GUESS YOU BELIEVE
YOU CAN FIGHT YOUR WAY
OUT OF HERE.

1152
01:29:37.238 --> 01:29:39.741
YOU GUESSED RIGHT.

1153
01:29:39.741 --> 01:29:42.243
I FOUND THE DEVICES.
I'VE TAKEN CARE OF THEM.

1154
01:29:44.245 --> 01:29:48.249
HEY !
GET THIS. BOYS.

1155
01:29:48.249 --> 01:29:50.752
YOU DISARMED THE BOMBS ?
WHAT DO YOU TAKE ME FOR ?

1156
01:29:51.252 --> 01:29:53.755
A MORON.
HOW ABOUT THIS ?

1157
01:29:54.756 --> 01:29:57.625
- [ Beeps ]  ONE.
- [ Crowd Screams ]

1158
01:29:58.760 --> 01:30:01.763
TWO. THREE !
DAMN IT !

1159
01:30:02.263 --> 01:30:06.267
I'M SICK
OF THIS GUY INTERFERING.
NOW PUT HIM AWAY.

1160
01:30:37.415 --> 01:30:39.917
[ Screaming ]
[ Wei Punches ]

1161
01:30:48.426 --> 01:30:52.930
[ Gibberish ]

1162
01:30:52.930 --> 01:30:54.932
- SAY. "AH."
- [ Groans ]

1163
01:30:55.433 --> 01:30:58.936
[ Groaning ]

1164
01:31:00.938 --> 01:31:02.573
[ Groaning ]

1165
01:31:06.694 --> 01:31:10.198
[ Yells ]

1166
01:31:14.202 --> 01:31:17.705
VERY GOOD.  VERY GOOD.

1167
01:31:17.705 --> 01:31:19.707
NOW THERE'S MORE MONEY
FOR ME.

1168
01:31:19.707 --> 01:31:23.211
- EVERYBODY. EVACUATE !
- [ Crowd Clamoring ]

1169
01:31:24.712 --> 01:31:27.715
- GET AFTER THEM !
- [ Throws Sticks ]

1170
01:32:07.638 --> 01:32:10.141
HOW MUCH DO THEY PAY YOU
FOR GETTING BEATEN
TO A PULP ?

1171
01:32:35.416 --> 01:32:38.419
[ Whoops. Yells ]

1172
01:33:05.563 --> 01:33:08.065
JUST GIVE US THE MONEY !

1173
01:33:09.567 --> 01:33:12.570
[ Bidders ]
IT'S ALL MINE. ALL OF IT !
IT'S NOT ALL YOURS !

1174
01:33:12.570 --> 01:33:14.071
GET AWAY FROM IT !
NO !  GIVE ME THAT !
NO. THAT'S MINE !

1175
01:33:14.071 --> 01:33:17.074
[ Arguing Continues ]
LOOK !
THAT'S MY MONEY.

1176
01:33:17.074 --> 01:33:19.577
[ Bidders Arguing ]

1177
01:33:44.101 --> 01:33:47.104
[ All Yell ]
OW. OW.

1178
01:33:51.609 --> 01:33:53.611
YOU DIE !  YOU DIE !

1179
01:33:56.614 --> 01:33:58.616
[ Thugs Yelling ]

1180
01:34:08.626 --> 01:34:11.128
BO !

1181
01:34:13.130 --> 01:34:15.132
[ Groaning ]

1182
01:34:22.640 --> 01:34:24.642
[ Chuckling ]

1183
01:34:25.643 --> 01:34:29.030
[ Johnny ]
HEY. JERKS !

1184
01:34:38.539 --> 01:34:40.041
[ Grunts ]

1185
01:34:40.541 --> 01:34:44.545
JOHNNY. BETTER GO NOW.
BUT. PAPA. I WANT
TO STAY HERE WITH YOU.

1186
01:34:44.545 --> 01:34:46.547
YOU SURE ABOUT IT ?
YOU BET.

1187
01:34:46.547 --> 01:34:49.050
[ Sighs ]

1188
01:34:49.050 --> 01:34:52.553
NEITHER OF YOU
HAVE SEEN MY BAD SIDE.

1189
01:34:54.055 --> 01:34:56.557
SO GET READY.

1190
01:35:00.561 --> 01:35:05.566
[ All Yelling ]

1191
01:35:34.595 --> 01:35:38.599
- [ All Grunting ]
- [ Gasps ]

1192
01:35:43.104 --> 01:35:48.109
[ Thugs Groaning. Gasping ]

1193
01:36:00.621 --> 01:36:03.624
[ Johnny Yelling ]

1194
01:36:07.128 --> 01:36:11.632
- [ Panting. Yells ]
- [ Johnny Yelling ]

1195
01:36:11.632 --> 01:36:15.136
[ Yelling ]

1196
01:36:34.155 --> 01:36:35.656
BO !

1197
01:36:37.658 --> 01:36:41.662
[ Gasping ]

1198
01:36:45.166 --> 01:36:47.168
[ Thug Punching Johnny ]

1199
01:36:50.171 --> 01:36:52.173
JOHNNY. THE LAST BOMB !

1200
01:36:57.795 --> 01:37:02.299
[ Laughing ]
I'M SO EXPLOSIVE.
NO ONE CAN STOP ME.

1201
01:37:02.299 --> 01:37:05.686
I CAN'T SEE. PAPA.

1202
01:37:07.188 --> 01:37:10.057
I'LL SEE BOTH
OF YOU IN HELL.

1203
01:37:10.057 --> 01:37:13.060
[ Helicopter Rotors Whirring ]

1204
01:37:13.060 --> 01:37:15.563
- [ Gasping ]
- [ Fires ]

1205
01:37:22.069 --> 01:37:25.072
COME ON.
WHAT ARE YOU WAITING FOR ?

1206
01:37:25.072 --> 01:37:27.575
DROP THE GUN.

1207
01:37:27.575 --> 01:37:30.077
[ Groaning ]
UH-HUH.

1208
01:37:35.583 --> 01:37:40.221
[ Johnny Continues Groaning ]

1209
01:37:40.221 --> 01:37:42.223
[ Laughing ]

1210
01:37:45.726 --> 01:37:49.730
COME ON.
SHOOT ME.

1211
01:37:49.730 --> 01:37:55.236
I'LL CHOKE HIM
TO DEATH.
SEA DRAGON.
CAN YOU HOLD ON ?

1212
01:37:55.736 --> 01:37:57.738
[ Johnny Coughing.
  Gagging ]

1213
01:37:58.239 --> 01:38:00.741
[ Weakly ]
JUST A LITTLE LONGER.

1214
01:38:04.745 --> 01:38:07.364
LITTLE BIT--

1215
01:38:08.365 --> 01:38:10.367
- [ Fires Gun ]
- [ Bo ]  OW !

1216
01:38:18.876 --> 01:38:21.378
JOHNNY !

1217
01:38:21.879 --> 01:38:24.381
JOHNNY !
COME ON.

1218
01:38:24.381 --> 01:38:26.884
COME ON !
HEY. JOHNNY !

1219
01:38:26.884 --> 01:38:29.386
HE'S NOT BREATHING.
WE GOT TO GET
OUT OF HERE !

1220
01:38:29.386 --> 01:38:31.388
THE HELICOPTER.

1221
01:38:37.895 --> 01:38:41.398
[ Helicopter Rotors
  Whirring ]

1222
01:38:43.400 --> 01:38:47.655
[ Whirring Continues ]
[ Wei Struggling ]

1223
01:38:49.657 --> 01:38:52.793
[ Yelling ]

1224
01:38:52.793 --> 01:38:56.797
[ Bomb Ticking ]

1225
01:38:56.797 --> 01:38:59.800
YOU'RE TOO LATE.

1226
01:38:59.800 --> 01:39:02.303
[ Gasping ]

1227
01:39:02.803 --> 01:39:04.805
[ Rotors Whirring ]

1228
01:39:04.805 --> 01:39:07.808
- KUNG WEI !
- [ Gasping ]

1229
01:39:08.309 --> 01:39:09.810
[ Ticking ]
[ Wei ]
GET GOING !

1230
01:39:10.311 --> 01:39:12.313
[ Bo. Wei Struggling ]

1231
01:39:12.313 --> 01:39:16.066
SAVE HIM !

1232
01:39:28.445 --> 01:39:29.446
[ Ticking ]
[ Bo. Wei Struggling ]

1233
01:39:29.446 --> 01:39:32.449
[ Gasping ]

1234
01:39:42.343 --> 01:39:44.845
[ Explosions Continue ]

1235
01:39:56.106 --> 01:39:59.109
[ Helicopter Departing ]

1236
01:39:59.426 --> 01:40:04.431
[ Siren Blares ]
GET AN I.V. GOING.
 GET THESE PEOPLE--

1237
01:40:04.431 --> 01:40:06.934
[ Siren Blaring ]

1238
01:40:06.934 --> 01:40:09.937
[ Siren Winds Down ]

1239
01:40:10.437 --> 01:40:12.940
REALLY ?
WHAT DOES YOUR PAPA SAY ?

1240
01:40:12.940 --> 01:40:15.442
HE SAYS THAT
WHEN A MAN TALKS.

1241
01:40:15.442 --> 01:40:17.444
A WOMAN'S SUPPOSED
TO PAY ATTENTION.

1242
01:40:18.946 --> 01:40:20.948
WHERE IS HE ?
WHERE'S MY SON ?

1243
01:40:22.950 --> 01:40:24.201
WHERE IS HE ?

1244
01:40:25.569 --> 01:40:27.454
[ Medical Personnel
  Talking ]

1245
01:40:28.455 --> 01:40:30.457
[ Wei ]
HAVE YOU SEEN MY SON ?

1246
01:40:36.213 --> 01:40:39.717
JOHNNY.

1247
01:40:39.717 --> 01:40:41.719
NO !

1248
01:40:44.221 --> 01:40:46.724
LISTEN. PAPA'S HERE.

1249
01:40:47.224 --> 01:40:49.226
JOHNNY. PLEASE--
[ Sobs ]

1250
01:40:49.226 --> 01:40:52.229
I'M SORRY.
YOUR BOY JUST
RAN OUT OF BREATH.

1251
01:40:52.730 --> 01:40:54.231
WHY DON'T YOU
DO SOMETHING ?

1252
01:40:54.732 --> 01:40:56.233
THERE'S NOTHING LEFT
TO DO.

1253
01:40:58.235 --> 01:41:01.739
JOHNNY ?  HE CAN'T DIE.
HE KNOWS KUNG FU BREATHING.

1254
01:41:03.741 --> 01:41:07.745
[ Crying ]
IT'S BECAUSE OF ME.

1255
01:41:08.245 --> 01:41:11.248
IT'S MY FAULT.
I'VE KILLED HIM.

1256
01:41:11.248 --> 01:41:16.754
STOP IT !
[ Coughing ]

1257
01:41:17.254 --> 01:41:19.373
[ Coughing Continues ]
JOHNNY !
HE'S OKAY !

1258
01:41:20.874 --> 01:41:23.377
YOU ALL RIGHT ?
OH !

1259
01:41:23.377 --> 01:41:26.880
[ Laughing ]

1260
01:41:26.880 --> 01:41:31.385
ANNA. YOUR KISSES
REMIND ME OF MOM'S.

1261
01:41:31.385 --> 01:41:33.387
BUT THAT'S OKAY.

1262
01:41:35.389 --> 01:41:37.391
OOH.

1263
01:41:37.391 --> 01:41:39.893
[ Chattering. Softly ]

1264
01:41:39.893 --> 01:41:42.896
[ Chattering Continues ]
CAN'T YOU SEE WE'RE TRYING
TO GET SOME FAMILY TIME ?

1265
01:41:48.402 --> 01:41:51.905
[ Both Laughing ]
[ Laughing ]
